  <para style="mt1">MARŨA MA MBERE MA PAŨLŨ KŨRĨ AKORINITHO</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Korinitho rĩarĩ itũũra inene, na rĩoĩkaine na maũndũ ma wonjoria, ũhũũri wa ũmaraya, na ndini cia mĩthemba mĩingĩ. Kanitha ũrĩa Paũlũ aambĩrĩirie Korinitho (Atũm 18) wakũrire ũthiũrũrũkĩirio nĩ maũndũ maya, na ũkĩambĩrĩria kũgayũkana nĩ ũndũ wa maũndũ maatiganĩte.</para>
  <para style="ip">Paũlũ aambĩrĩirie na kũmaandĩkĩra maũndũ marĩa maagayũkanagia Kanitha. Maũndũ macio maarĩ:</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓ciũria ciakoniĩ kĩhiko,</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓irio iria ciarutagĩrwo mĩhianano,</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓iheo cia kĩĩroho,</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓maũndũ makoniĩ kũriũka.</para>
  <para style="ip">Paũlũ nĩerire andũ a Korinitho atĩ wendo nĩguo warĩ ũndũ wa bata mũno gũkĩra maũndũ marĩa mangĩ. Nĩameerire atĩ mangĩaikaraga mendanĩte nĩmangĩahotaga gũtooria mathĩĩna marĩa maakoragwo kanitha-inĩ (13:4-8).</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ Mũtũmwo Paũlũ.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Ngeithi cia Paũlũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 1:1-9">1:1-9</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Thĩĩna wa njatũkano <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 1:10-4:21">1:10–4:21</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Thĩĩna wa andũ gũkomania na andũ arĩa maatarainie <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 5:1-13">5:1-13</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Thĩĩna ũkoniĩ maciira igooti-inĩ <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 6:1-11">6:1-11</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Thĩĩna wa ũtharia wa andũ matahikanĩtie <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 6:12-20">6:12-20</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mathĩĩna makoniĩ ũhoro wa gũtũũrania thuutha wa andũ kũhikania <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 7:1-40">7:1-40</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mathĩĩna makoniĩ mĩhianano <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 8:1-11:1">8:1–11:1</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mathĩĩna makoniĩ mũhoere <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 11:2-14:40">11:2–14:40</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mathĩĩna makoniĩ ũhoro wa andũ kũriũka <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 15:1-58">15:1-58</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ciugo cia kũrĩkĩrĩria <char style="ior"><ref loc="1CO 16:1-24">16:1-24</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:1">Arom 1:1</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 1:1">2Akor 1:1</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 8:17">Atũm 8:17</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ niĩ Paũlũ, o niĩ ndeetirwo nduĩke mũtũmwo wa Kristũ Jesũ nĩ ũndũ wa kwenda kwa Ngai, ndĩratũma ngeithi ici tũrĩ hamwe na mũrũ wa Ithe witũ Sosithene,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1:1 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Warĩ mũtugo wa Ayunani kwambĩrĩria marũa na rĩĩtwa rĩa mwandĩki.</char></note></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 10:32">1Akor 10:32</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 18:1">Atũm 18:1</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 1:7">Arom 1:7</ref></char>
    </note>Twandĩkĩra kanitha wa Ngai ũrĩa ũrĩ Korinitho, kũrĩ arĩa othe maamũrĩtwo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ na magetwo matuĩke andũ atheru, o hamwe na arĩa othe marĩ kũndũ guothe makayagĩra rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani witũ Jesũ Kristũ, o we Mwathani wao na witũ:</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Wega na thayũ irogĩa kũrĩ inyuĩ ciumĩte kũrĩ Ngai Ithe witũ na Mwathani Jesũ Kristũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũcookia Ngaatho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:8">Arom 1:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩnjookagĩria Ngai ngaatho hĩndĩ ciothe nĩ ũndũ wanyu, nĩ ũndũ wa wega wake ũrĩa mũheetwo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 9:11">2Akor 9:11</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo thĩinĩ wake nĩmũtongetio maũndũ-inĩ mothe, mũgatongio ũhoro-inĩ wa mĩario yanyu yothe o na ũhoro-inĩ wothe wa kũmenya maũndũ, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="REV 1:2">Kũg 1:2</ref></char></note>tondũ-rĩ, ũira witũ ũkoniĩ Kristũ nĩwekĩrirwo hinya thĩinĩ wanyu. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:7">Math 16:7</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 3:12">2Pet 3:12</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio gũtirĩ kĩheo gĩa kĩĩroho o na kĩmwe mũtarĩ nakĩo, o mũgĩetagĩrĩra na kĩyo kũguũranĩrio kwa Mwathani witũ Jesũ Kristũ. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Nake nĩarĩmũikaragia mũrĩ na hinya nginya mũthia, nĩguo mũtikanakorwo mũrĩ na ũcuuke mũthenya ũrĩa wa Mwathani witũ Jesũ Kristũ. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:28">Arom 8:28</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 1:3">1Joh 1:3</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 49:7">Isa 49:7</ref></char></note>Ngai nĩ mwĩhokeku, o we ũrĩa wamwĩtire nĩguo mũkorwo na ngwatanĩro na Mũriũ Jesũ Kristũ, Mwathani witũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Nyamũkano thĩinĩ wa Kanitha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>Atĩrĩrĩ, inyuĩ ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ndamũthaitha thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani witũ Jesũ Kristũ, atĩ inyuothe mũiguane o mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ, nĩguo mũtikagĩe na nyamũkano gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu, no mũikare mũiguanĩte, na mũrĩ na meciiria o mamwe, na ngoro o ĩmwe. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Tondũ rĩĩrĩ ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, nĩmenyithĩtio nĩ andũ amwe a kuuma nyũmba ya Kiloe atĩ nĩ kũrĩ na ngũĩ gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ũrĩa ndĩroiga nĩ atĩrĩ: Ũmwe wanyu oigaga atĩ, “Niĩ nũmagĩrĩra Paũlũ”; ũngĩ akoiga atĩ, “Niĩ nũmagĩrĩra Apolo”; nake ũngĩ akoiga atĩ, “Niĩ nũmagĩrĩra Kefa”; o na ningĩ ũngĩ akoiga atĩ, “Niĩ nũmagĩrĩra Kristũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 28:19">Math 28:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kaĩ Kristũ agayanĩtio? Paũlũ-rĩ, nĩwe waambirwo mũtĩ igũrũ nĩ ũndũ wanyu? Mwabatithirio thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Paũlũ? <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:8">Atũm 18:8</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 19:29">Atũm 19:29</ref></char></note>Nĩngũcookia ngaatho nĩ ũndũ gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wanyu niĩ ndaabatithirie, o tiga Kirisipo na Gayo. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũmwe ũngiuga atĩ mwabatithirio thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩakwa. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 11:14">Atũm 11:14</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 16:15">1Akor 16:15</ref></char></note>Ĩĩ, o na ningĩ nĩndabatithirie andũ a nyũmba ya Stefana; no tiga acio, ndingĩririkana kana nĩ kũrĩ mũndũ ũngĩ ndaabatithirie. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nĩ gũkorwo Kristũ ndaandũmire ngabatithanie, no aandũmire ngahunjie Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega, no ti ndĩũheane na ũũgĩ wa mũndũ, nĩgeetha mũtharaba wa Kristũ ndũkae kwagithio kĩene.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kristũ nĩwe Ũũgĩ na Ũhoti wa Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TH 2:10">2Athe 2:10</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 1:16">Arom 1:16</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo ndũmĩrĩri ya mũtharaba nĩ ũrimũ kũrĩ arĩa maroora, no kũrĩ ithuĩ arĩa tũrahonokio-rĩ, ũndũ ũcio nĩ hinya wa Ngai. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 29:14">Isa 29:14</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ũũgĩ wa andũ arĩa oogĩ nĩkũniina ngaaũniina;</para>
  <para style="q2">naguo ũmenyo wa andũ arĩa imenyi ndĩkĩũtue wa tũhũ.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa mũũgĩ-rĩ, akĩrĩ kũ? Mũndũ ũrĩa mũthomu-rĩ, akĩrĩ kũ? Arĩ ha mũciiri ũrĩa ũũĩ gũciira maũndũ ma mahinda maya tũrĩ? Githĩ Ngai ndatuĩte ũũgĩ wa thĩ ĩno ũrimũ? <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:14">Arom 11:14</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Ngai na ũndũ wa ũũgĩ wake nĩonire atĩ andũ a thĩ ĩno na ũũgĩ wao matikaamũmenya, akĩona kwagĩrĩire ahũthĩre maũndũ ma ũrimũ marĩa tũhunjagia nĩgeetha ahonokie arĩa mamwĩtĩkagia. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:38">Math 12:38</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:11">Joh 2:11</ref></char></note>Ayahudi metagia ciama, nao Ayunani macaragia ũũgĩ, <verse number="23" style="v"/>no ithuĩ tũhunjagia ũhoro wa Kristũ arĩ mwambe mũtĩ igũrũ: maũndũ macio nĩ mũhĩnga kũrĩ Ayahudi na ũrimũ kũrĩ andũ-a-Ndũrĩrĩ, <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:16">Arom 1:16</ref>; <ref loc="COL 2:3">Akol 2:3</ref></char></note>no kũrĩ arĩa Ngai etĩte, Ayahudi o na Ayunani, Kristũ nĩwe hinya wa Ngai na ũũgĩ wa Ngai. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo ũrimũ wa Ngai nĩ mũũgĩ gũkĩra ũũgĩ wa mũndũ, naguo ũhũthũ wa Ngai nĩ mũritũ gũkĩra hinya wa mũndũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ta gĩciiriei ũrĩa mwatariĩ rĩrĩa mwetirwo. Ti aingĩ anyu oogĩ na ũũgĩ wa andũ a gũkũ thĩ; na ti aingĩ mangĩaguucĩrĩirie andũ; o na ti aingĩ maciarĩirwo mĩciĩ ĩrĩa ĩrĩ igweta. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:22">Arom 1:22</ref></char></note>No Ngai aathuurire maũndũ marĩa ma ũrimũ ma thĩ ĩno nĩguo aconorithie andũ arĩa oogĩ; ningĩ Ngai aathuurire maũndũ marĩa matarĩ hinya ma thĩ ĩno nĩguo aconorithie arĩa marĩ hinya. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Agĩthuura maũndũ marĩa mahũthũ ma thĩ ĩno, na marĩa matarĩ ma gũtĩĩka, o gwata marĩa matarĩ maũndũ kũrĩ, nĩgeetha amaagithie bata, <verse number="29" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:29 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:9">Aef 2:9</ref></char></note>nĩgeetha mũndũ o na ũ ndakanetĩĩe mbere ya Ngai. <verse number="30" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, nĩwe ũtũmĩte mũkorwo mũrĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ, ũrĩa ũtuĩkĩte ũũgĩ uumĩte kũrĩ Ngai nĩ ũndũ witũ, ũguo nĩ kuuga, ũthingu witũ, na ũtheru, na gũkũũrwo. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 9:23">Jer 9:23</ref>, <ref loc="JER 9:24">24</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, o ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: “Mũndũ ũrĩa ũkwĩraha, nĩerahage nĩ ũndũ wa Mwathani.”</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 1:17">1Akor 1:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndookire kũrĩ inyuĩ, ngĩmũhunjĩria ũira wa hitho ya ũhoro wa Ngai, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ndiamwarĩirie na mĩario ya kanua kega kana ũũgĩ mũnene. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 6:14">Agal 6:14</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩndatuĩte itua ndirĩ ũndũ ũngĩ ngwenda kũmenya, rĩrĩa rĩothe ndaarĩ na inyuĩ, o tiga ũhoro wa Jesũ Kristũ na kwambwo gwake mũtĩ-igũrũ. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:1-18">Atũm 18:1-18</ref></char></note>Ndookire kũrĩ inyuĩ itarĩ na hinya, na ndĩ na guoya, o na ngĩinainaga mũno. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ndũmĩrĩri yakwa na kũhunjia gwakwa itiarĩ na ciugo cia kũguucanĩrĩria na ũũgĩ, no nĩcionanagia hinya wa Roho, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 4:7">2Akor 4:7</ref></char></note>nĩguo wĩtĩkio wanyu ndũgakorwo ũtiirĩrĩirwo nĩ ũũgĩ wa andũ, o tiga hinya wa Ngai.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũũgĩ Uumanĩte na Roho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 1:20">1Akor 1:20</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 146:4">Thab 146:4</ref></char>
    </note>No ningĩ ithuĩ-rĩ, tũrĩ gatagatĩ-inĩ ka andũ arĩa agima twaragia ũhoro wa ndũmĩrĩri ya ũũgĩ, no tũtiaragia ũhoro wa ũũgĩ wa mahinda maya, kana wa aathani a mahinda maya arĩa matarĩ kũrĩa merekeire. <verse number="7" style="v"/>No ithuĩ-rĩ, twaragia ũhoro wa ũũgĩ wa Ngai ũrĩa wa hitho, ũũgĩ ũrĩa watũire ũrĩ mũhithe, o ũrĩa Ngai aathĩrĩire o mbere ya kũũmba thĩ nĩ ũndũ wa riiri witũ. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 24:7">Thab 24:7</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ o na ũmwe wa anene a mahinda maya wamenyire ũhoro ũcio, nĩgũkorwo mangĩaũmenyete-rĩ, matingĩaambire Mwathani wa riiri. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 64:4">Isa 64:4</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo no ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Maũndũ marĩa matarĩ monwo na maitho,</para>
  <para style="q2">na matarĩ maiguuo na matũ,</para>
  <para style="q1">o na matarĩ maatoonya ngoro ya mũndũ,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩmo Ngai athondekeire andũ arĩa mamwendete”:</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>no Ngai nĩatũguũrĩirie maũndũ macio na ũndũ wa Roho wake.</para>
  <para style="p">Roho nĩathuthuuragia maũndũ mothe, o na maũndũ ma Ngai marĩa marikĩru mũno. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 17:9">Jer 17:9</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 20:27">Thim 20:27</ref></char></note>Tondũ-rĩ, nũũ ũũĩ meciiria ma mũndũ, tiga o roho wa mũndũ ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wake? O ta ũguo-rĩ, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũũĩ meciiria ma Ngai, o tiga Roho wa Ngai. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:15">Arom 8:15</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 2:5">Jak 2:5</ref></char></note>Tũtiamũkĩrĩte roho wa thĩ ĩno, no tũheetwo Roho ũrĩa uumĩte kũrĩ Ngai, nĩguo tũmenyage iheo iria Ngai atũheete o ũguo tũhũ. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Maũndũ macio nĩmo twaragia, no tũtimaaragia na ciugo iria tũrutĩtwo na ũũgĩ wa mũndũ, no nĩ na ciugo iria tũrutagwo nĩ Roho, tũgataarĩria ũhoro wa ma wa kĩĩroho na ciugo cia kĩĩroho. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:18">1Akor 1:18</ref></char></note>Mũndũ ũtarĩ na Roho ndetĩkagĩra maũndũ marĩa moimaga kũrĩ Roho wa Ngai, tondũ maũndũ macio nĩ ũrimũ kũrĩ we, na ndangĩmamenya, tondũ makũũrĩkanaga na njĩra ya kĩĩroho. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Mũndũ wa kĩĩroho nĩakũũranaga maũndũ mothe, nowe mwene gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩmũtuĩra:</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>“Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩmenya meciiria ma Mwathani,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩguo akĩmũtaare?”</para>
  <para style="m">No ithuĩ tũrĩ na meciiria ma Kristũ.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ũhoro wa Nyamũkano thĩinĩ wa Kanitha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 2:15">1Akor 2:15</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 2:14">1Akor 2:14</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 14:20">1Akor 14:20</ref></char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ndingĩahotire kũmwarĩria ta mũrĩ andũ a kĩĩroho, no ndaamwarĩirie ta mũrĩ andũ a thĩ, o ta twana tũnini thĩinĩ wa Kristũ. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 5:12-14">Ahib 5:12-14</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 2:2">1Pet 2:2</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 16:12">Joh 16:12</ref></char></note>Ndaamũheire iria, no ti irio nyũmũ ndaamũheire, nĩgũkorwo mũtiakinyĩte a gũcirĩa. Ti-itherũ o na rĩu mũtikinyĩte a gũcirĩa. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 5:20">Agal 5:20</ref></char></note>O na rĩu mũrĩ andũ a thĩ. Kuona atĩ kũrĩ na ũiru na ngũĩ thĩinĩ wanyu-rĩ, githĩ mũtikĩrĩ andũ a thĩ? Githĩ mũtiragĩĩka o ta ũrĩa andũ a ndũire mekaga? <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, rĩrĩa mũndũ ũmwe ekuuga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nũmagĩrĩra Paũlũ,” nake ũrĩa ũngĩ akoiga atĩrĩ, “Niĩ nũmagĩrĩra Apolo,” githĩ mũtikĩrĩ o andũ a ndũire?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 18:24">Atũm 18:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kaĩ Apolo akĩrĩ ũ? Nake Paũlũ akĩrĩ ũ? Acio maarĩ o ndungata, iria ciatũmire mwĩtĩkie, o ta ũrĩa Mwathani aagaĩire o mũndũ wĩra wake. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:4-11">Atũm 18:4-11</ref></char></note>Niĩ nĩ mbeũ ndahaandire, nake Apolo agĩciitĩrĩria maaĩ, no nĩ Ngai watũmire ikũre. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ti mũndũ ũrĩa ũhaandaga kana ũrĩa ũitagĩrĩria maaĩ ũrĩ bata, no ũrĩa ũrĩ bata nĩ Ngai, ũrĩa ũtũmaga ikũre. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa ũhaandaga na mũndũ ũrĩa ũitagĩrĩria maaĩ makoragwo na muoroto ũmwe, na o mũndũ akaarĩhwo kũringana na wĩra wake we mwene. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 6:1">2Akor 6:1</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 61:3">Isa 61:3</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:20-22">Aef 2:20-22</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo tũrutithanagia wĩra hamwe na Ngai; na inyuĩ mũrĩ mũgũnda wa Ngai, na mwako wa Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:3">Arom 12:3</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 15:20">Arom 15:20</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa wega ũrĩa Ngai aaheete, niĩ nĩ gwaka ndaakire mũthingi haana ta mwakithia ũrĩa mũũgĩ nake mũndũ ũngĩ nĩ gwaka araaka igũrũ rĩa mũthingi ũcio. No o mũndũ nĩamenyagĩrĩre ũrĩa egwaka igũrũ rĩaguo. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:20">Aef 2:20</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩaka mũthingi ũngĩ tiga ũrĩa ũrĩkĩtie gwakwo, na nĩguo Jesũ Kristũ. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo mũndũ o na ũ egwaka igũrũ rĩa mũthingi ũyũ akĩhũthagĩra thahabu, kana betha, kana mahiga ma goro, kana mbaũ, kana nyeki, o na kana rũũa-rĩ, <verse number="13" style="v"/>wĩra wake nĩũkoneka ũrĩa ũtariĩ, tondũ Mũthenya ũcio nĩũgaatũma woneke ũtheri-inĩ. Wĩra ũcio ũkaaguũrio na mwaki, nĩgũkorwo wĩra wa o mũndũ nĩũkagerio na mwaki ũcio. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo kĩrĩa mũndũ aakĩte mũthingi-igũrũ nĩgĩgetiiria mwaki ũcio-rĩ, nĩakarĩhwo mũcaara wake. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JUD 1:23">Jud 23</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo nĩũkahĩa-rĩ, nĩakoorwo nĩguo; nowe mwene nĩakahonoka, no akaahonoka ta mũndũ ũgereire mwaki-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 6:16">2Akor 6:16</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:9">Arom 8:9</ref></char>
    </note>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ inyuĩ ene mũrĩ hekarũ ya Ngai, na atĩ Roho wa Ngai atũũraga thĩinĩ wanyu? <verse number="17" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe angĩananga hekarũ ya Ngai-rĩ, Ngai nĩakamwananga; nĩgũkorwo hekarũ ya Ngai nĩ theru, na nĩ inyuĩ hekarũ ĩyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Mũtikae kwĩheenia. Mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ thĩinĩ wanyu angĩkorwo nĩeciiragia nĩ mũũgĩ na ũũgĩ wa mahinda maya tũrĩ-rĩ, nĩagĩtuĩke “kĩrimũ” nĩguo atuĩke mũũgĩ. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:22">Arom 1:22</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 5:13">Ayub 5:13</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ũũgĩ wa thĩ ĩno nĩ ũrimũ maitho-inĩ ma Ngai. O ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ, “Nĩanyiitaga arĩa oogĩ waara-inĩ wao”; <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 94:11">Thab 94:11</ref></char></note>o na ningĩ nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ, “Mwathani nĩoĩ atĩ meciiria ma arĩa oogĩ nĩ ma tũhũ.” <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:32">Arom 8:32</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ndakae kwĩraha na ũhoro wa andũ! Maũndũ mothe nĩ manyu, <verse number="22" style="v"/>kana nĩ Paũlũ, kana nĩ Apolo, kana nĩ Kefa, kana nĩ thĩ ĩno, kana nĩ muoyo, kana nĩ gĩkuũ, kana nĩ maũndũ marĩa marĩ ho rĩu, kana nĩ maũndũ marĩa magooka, mothe nĩ manyu, <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 10:7">2Akor 10:7</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 3:29">Agal 3:29</ref></char></note>na inyuĩ mũrĩ a Kristũ, nake Kristũ nĩ wa Ngai.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Atũmwo a Kristũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, andũ magĩrĩirwo nĩgũtuonaga ta ndungata cia Kristũ, na ta tũrĩ andũ arĩa mehokeirwo maũndũ ma hitho ma Ngai. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Rĩu nĩkũbataranĩtie atĩ andũ arĩa mehokeirwo maũndũ no nginya monanie atĩ nĩ ehokeku. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ndingĩmaka o na hanini ingĩtuĩrwo ciira nĩ inyuĩ, kana nduĩrwo nĩ igooti rĩa andũ o na rĩrĩkũ; ti-itherũ o na niĩ mwene ndingĩĩtuĩra ciira. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 2:13">Arom 2:13</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 10:18">2Akor 10:18</ref></char></note>Niĩ mwene ndirĩ na ũndũ ingĩĩcuukĩra, no ũndũ ũcio ndũngĩtũma nduĩke atĩ ndirĩ na mahĩtia. Mwathani nĩwe ũnduagĩra ciira. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 12:22">Ayub 12:22</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 2:29">Arom 2:29</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndũkae gũtua ciira ihinda rĩrĩa rĩamũre rĩtakinyĩte; eterera nginya Mwathani ooke. Maũndũ marĩa mahithe nduma-inĩ nĩakamoimĩria ũtheri-inĩ, na nĩakaguũria meciiria ma ngoro cia andũ. Ihinda rĩu o mũndũ nĩakamũkĩra ngaatho ciake kuuma kũrĩ Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Rĩu-rĩ, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, maũndũ macio ndĩramaringithania na ũhoro wakwa mwene na wa Apolo nĩguo mũgunĩke, nĩguo mwĩrute na ithuĩ gĩtũmi kĩa ũrĩa kwĩragwo atĩrĩ, “Mũtikae kwagarara ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo.” Nĩgeetha mũtikae gwĩtĩĩa mũndũ ũmwe makĩria ya ũrĩa ũngĩ. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, nũũ ũtũmĩte wĩone ũrĩ na ngũũrani na mũndũ ũngĩ o wothe? Nĩ kĩĩ ũrĩ nakĩo ũtaaheirwo? Na angĩkorwo nĩwaheirwo-rĩ, ũragĩĩtĩĩa nĩkĩ ta atarĩ kũheo waheirwo?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 3:17">Kũg 3:17</ref>, <ref loc="REV 3:18">18</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩmũrĩkĩtie kũgĩa na kĩrĩa gĩothe mwendaga! Nĩmũrĩkĩtie gũtonga! Nĩmũtuĩkĩte athamaki, ithuĩ tũtarĩ ho! Naarĩ korwo ti-itherũ nĩmwatuĩkire athamaki kũna nĩguo tũtuĩke a gũthamaka hamwe na inyuĩ! <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 10:33">Ahib 10:33</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ndĩrona atĩ ithuĩ atũmwo Ngai atũigĩte handũ tũrĩonekaga tũrĩ thuutha wa andũ arĩa angĩ othe, na ta andũ matuĩrĩirwo kũũragĩrwo thĩinĩ wa kĩhaaro kĩa mathako. Nĩtũtuĩtwo kĩndũ gĩa kwĩrorerwo nĩ thĩ yothe, kũrĩ araika o na kũrĩ andũ. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 17:18">Atũm 17:18</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 3:18">1Akor 3:18</ref></char></note>Ithuĩ tũrĩ irimũ nĩ ũndũ wa Kristũ, no inyuĩ mũrĩ andũ oogĩ mũno thĩinĩ wa Kristũ! Ithuĩ nĩ kwaga twagĩte hinya, no inyuĩ mũrĩ na hinya! Inyuĩ nĩmũheetwo gĩtĩĩo, no ithuĩ nĩtũimĩtwo gĩtĩĩo! <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:35">Arom 8:35</ref></char></note>Nginya ihinda rĩĩrĩ ithuĩ tũrĩ tũtũũrĩte tũhũũtaga na tũkanyoota, na tũgatarũkĩrwo nĩ nguo, ningĩ nĩtũhũũrĩtwo mũno, o na tũgaikara tũtarĩ na mĩciĩ. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:3">Atũm 18:3</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 3:9">1Pet 3:9</ref></char></note>Ningĩ nĩtũrutaga wĩra na moko maitũ tũrĩ na kĩyo. Rĩrĩa twarumwo-rĩ, ithuĩ tũkarathima; na rĩrĩa twanyariirwo, tũkomĩrĩria; <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JER 20:18">Jer 20:18</ref></char></note>o na rĩrĩa twacambio, tũcookagia ũhoro na ũhooreri. Nginya ihinda rĩĩrĩ tũtuĩkĩte gĩko gĩa thĩ, tũgatuĩka mahuti ma gũkũ thĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 6:15">1Akor 6:15</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 2:11">1Athe 2:11</ref></char>
    </note>Ndiraandĩka marũa maya nĩguo ndĩmũconore, no nĩguo ndĩmũtaare mũrĩ ta ciana ciakwa nyendete mũno. <verse number="15" style="v"/>O na mũngĩkorwo mũrĩ na areri ngiri ikũmi thĩinĩ wa Kristũ, mũtirĩ na maithe maingĩ, nĩgũkorwo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ ndaatuĩkire ithe wanyu ũndũ-inĩ wa Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 11:1">1Akor 11:1</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 1:6">1Athe 1:6</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndamũthaitha mwĩgerekanie na niĩ. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:1">Atũm 16:1</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 7:17">1Akor 7:17</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gĩtũmi gĩkĩ nĩngũmũtũmĩra Timotheo, mũrũ wakwa ũrĩa nyendete, na ũrĩa mwĩhokeku thĩinĩ wa Mwathani. Nĩekũmũririkania mũtũũrĩre wakwa thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ, ũrĩa ũringaine na ũrĩa ndutanaga makanitha-inĩ kũndũ guothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Amwe anyu nĩmatuĩkĩte etĩĩi, makona ta itarooka kũu kũrĩ inyuĩ. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:21">Atũm 18:21</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 1:15">2Akor 1:15</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 1:16">16</ref></char></note>No nĩngũũka kũrĩ inyuĩ narua, akorwo nĩ kwenda kwa Mwathani, na hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩngatuĩria ũrĩa andũ aya etĩĩi maaragia, o hamwe na ũhoti ũrĩa marĩ naguo. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo ũthamaki wa Ngai ti ũhoro wa kwaria, no nĩ wa kũgĩa na ũhoti. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 1:23">2Akor 1:23</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 13:2">2Akor 13:2</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 13:10">10</ref></char></note>Mũkwenda atĩa? Ngĩũke kũrĩ inyuĩ na kĩboko, kana njũke na wendo hamwe na roho wa ũhooreri?</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ingatai Mũndũ ũcio Gĩtharia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 18:8">Alaw 18:8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ma ndeto nĩiraario atĩ thĩinĩ wanyu kũrĩ na ũtharia, na nĩ ũtharia mũthemba ũrĩa ũtangĩoneka o na kũrĩ andũ arĩa matetĩkĩtie Ngai: Naguo nĩ atĩ ũmwe wanyu nĩakomete na mũtumia wa ithe. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 7:7-11">2Akor 7:7-11</ref></char></note>Na inyuĩ mũgakenera ũndũ ũcio! Githĩ mũtiagĩrĩirwo nĩgũkorwo mũiyũrĩtwo nĩ kĩeha, nĩguo mũndũ ũcio wĩkĩte ũguo mũmũingate, ehere ngwatanĩro-inĩ yanyu? <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 2:5">Akol 2:5</ref></char></note>O na ndakorwo ndirĩ hamwe na inyuĩ kũu, ndĩ hamwe na inyuĩ thĩinĩ wa roho, na nĩndĩkĩtie gũtuĩra mũndũ ũcio wĩkĩte ũguo ciira, o ta ndĩ hamwe na inyuĩ. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 3:6">2Athe 3:6</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũrĩkorwo mũnganĩte thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani witũ Jesũ, na niĩ ndĩ hamwe na inyuĩ thĩinĩ wa roho, o na hinya wa Mwathani witũ Jesũ ũrĩ ho-rĩ, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:20">1Tim 1:20</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:10">Math 4:10</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 1:8">1Akor 1:8</ref></char></note>mũndũ ũcio mũneanei kũrĩ Shaitani, nĩgeetha mehia make ma kĩĩmwĩrĩ maniinwo, naguo roho wake ũkaahonokio mũthenya ũrĩa wa Mwathani.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 4:6">Jak 4:6</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 5:9">Agal 5:9</ref></char>
    </note>Mwĩgaatho ũcio wanyu ti mwega. Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ ndawa nini ya kũimbia mĩgate nĩĩtũmaga kĩmere gĩothe kĩimbe? <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 1:19">1Pet 1:19</ref></char></note>Eheriai ndawa ĩyo ya kũimbia mĩgate ĩrĩa ya tene biũ nĩguo mũtuĩke kĩmere kĩerũ gĩtarĩ na ndawa ya kũimbia, tondũ ũguo nĩguo mũtariĩ. Nĩgũkorwo Kristũ, o we gatũrũme gaitũ ka Bathaka, nĩarĩkĩtie kũrutwo igongona. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 12:14">Thaam 12:14</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, nĩtũkũngũĩre Gĩathĩ, ti na ndawa ĩyo ya tene ya kũimbia mĩgate, ĩyo ya rũmena na ya waganu, no tũkũngũĩre na mũgate ũtarĩ na ndawa ya kũimbia, o guo mũgate wa wĩhokeku na wa ũhoro wa ma.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 5:11">Aef 5:11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩndĩmwandĩkĩire marũa-inĩ makwa ngamwĩra mũtigage kũgĩaga thiritũ na andũ arĩa ahũũri maraya, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:27">1Akor 10:27</ref></char></note>ũguo ti kuuga mweheranĩre na andũ a thĩ ĩno, arĩa ahũũri maraya, kana arĩa akoroku, kana arĩa atunyani, o na kana arĩa ahooi mĩhianano. Mũngĩĩka ũguo-rĩ, no mũkiumire gũkũ thĩ. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 7:1">Arom 7:1</ref></char></note>No rĩu, ndĩramwandĩkĩra nĩguo mũtikagĩe thiritũ na mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ũrĩa wĩĩtaga mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ, no nĩ mũhũũri maraya, kana nĩ mũkoroku, kana nĩ mũhooi mĩhianano kana nĩ mũndũ wa gũcambania, o na kana nĩ mũrĩĩu wa njoohi kana nĩ mũtunyani. Mũndũ ta ũcio mũtikarĩĩanĩre nake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 4:11">Mar 4:11</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 6:1-4">1Akor 6:1-4</ref></char>
    </note>Ũkĩrĩ wĩra wakwa gũciirithia arĩa matarĩ a kanitha? Githĩ inyuĩ mũtikĩagĩrĩirwo nĩgũciirithia arĩa marĩ a kanitha? <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 13:5">Gũcook 13:5</ref></char></note>Ngai nĩwe ũgaaciirithia arĩa marĩ nja. “Ingatai mũndũ ũcio mwaganu oime thĩinĩ wanyu.”</para>
  <chapter number="6" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Maciira Gatagatĩ-inĩ ka Andũ Etĩkia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Kũngĩkorwo kũrĩ mũndũ ũmwe wanyu ũhĩtĩirie ũrĩa ũngĩ-rĩ, no akĩgerie gũthiĩ kũrĩ andũ arĩa matetigĩrĩte Ngai nĩguo mamatuithanie ciira, handũ ha gũthiĩ mbere ya andũ arĩa aamũre? <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 19:28">Math 19:28</ref></char></note>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ andũ arĩa aamũre nĩo magaatuĩra andũ a gũkũ thĩ ciira? Na angĩkorwo nĩ inyuĩ mũgaaciirithia andũ a gũkũ thĩ-rĩ, githĩ mũtikĩrĩ na ũhoti wa gũtua maciira marĩa manini? <verse number="3" style="v"/>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ nĩ ithuĩ tũgaatuĩra araika ciira? Ĩ maũndũ ma mũtũũrĩre ũyũ-rĩ, githĩ tũtiagĩrĩirwo nĩkũmaciira makĩria! <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio kũngĩkorwo na mũndũ wanyu ũhĩtĩirio maũndũ-inĩ ta macio-rĩ, no mũthuure o na andũ matangĩtĩĩka kanitha-inĩ matuĩke a kũmũciirithia! <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 1:15">Atũm 1:15</ref></char></note>Ndoiga ũguo nĩguo ndĩmũconore. Kwahoteka atĩa atĩ thĩinĩ wanyu gũtirĩ mũndũ mũũgĩ ũngĩhota gũtuithania etĩkia eerĩ ciira mangĩhĩtania? <verse number="6" style="v"/>No handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ atwaraga ũrĩa ũngĩ igooti-inĩ, na nĩ igooti-inĩ rĩa arĩa matetĩkĩtie!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:39">Math 5:39</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 5:40">40</ref></char>
    </note>Gũkorwo mũrĩ na maciira gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu nĩkuonania atĩ nĩmũhootetwo biũ. Githĩ ti kaba mwĩtĩkagĩre gwĩkwo ũũru? Githĩ ti kaba mwĩtĩkagĩre kũheenio? <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 4:6">1Athe 4:6</ref></char></note>Handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, nĩmũheenanagia na mũgekana ũũru, na acio mwĩkaga ũguo-rĩ, nĩ ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe wanyu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ andũ arĩa aaganu matikagaya ũthamaki wa Ngai? Mũtikanaheeneke: Gũtirĩ ahũũri maraya, kana ahooi mĩhianano, kana itharia, kana arũme arĩa metuaga ta aka, kana arũme arĩa makomaga na arũme arĩa angĩ, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="REV 21:8">Kũg 21:8</ref></char></note>kana aici, kana andũ arĩa akoroku, kana arĩĩu, kana acambania, o na kana atunyani makaagaya ũthamaki wa Ngai. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Na ũguo nĩguo amwe anyu mwatariĩ. No nĩmwathambirio, na mũgĩtherio, na mũgĩtuuo athingu thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani Jesũ Kristũ o na nĩ ũndũ wa Roho wa Ngai witũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mehia ma Ũtharia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 10:23">1Akor 10:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Niĩ ndirigĩrĩirio gwĩka ũndũ o wothe,” no ti ũndũ o wothe ũrĩ kĩguni. “Niĩ ndirigĩrĩirio gwĩka ũndũ o wothe,” no ndingĩathwo nĩ ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ. <verse number="13" style="v"/>“Irio nĩ cia nda na nda nĩ ya irio,” no Ngai nĩagaciniina cierĩ. Mwĩrĩ ti wa kũhũthĩrwo na ũmaraya, no nĩ wa gũtungata Mwathani, nake Mwathani aathage mwĩrĩ ũcio. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 6:5">Arom 6:5</ref></char></note>Ngai nĩariũkirie Mwathani kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ nĩ ũndũ wa hinya wake, na o na ithuĩ nĩagatũriũkia na hinya o ro ũcio. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:5">Arom 12:5</ref></char></note>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ mĩĩrĩ yanyu nĩ ciĩga cia Kristũ we mwene? Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, no ngĩoye ciĩga icio cia Kristũ nĩguo ndĩcinyiitithanie na mũmaraya? Kũroaga gũtuĩka ũguo! <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 2:24">Kĩam 2:24</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 19:5">Math 19:5</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 5:31">Aef 5:31</ref></char></note>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ mũndũ ũrĩa wĩnyiitithanagia na mũmaraya, matuĩkaga mwĩrĩ ũmwe nake? Nĩgũkorwo nĩ kwĩrĩtwo atĩrĩ, “Acio eerĩ magaatuĩka mwĩrĩ ũmwe.” <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 17:21-23">Joh 17:21-23</ref></char></note>No mũndũ ũrĩa wĩnyiitithanagia na Mwathani atuĩkaga ũmwe nake thĩinĩ wa roho.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">6:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 13:4">Ahib 13:4</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 6:12">Arom 6:12</ref></char>
    </note>Ũragĩrai mehia ma ũmaraya. Mehia marĩa mangĩ mothe mekagwo nĩ mũndũ marĩ nja ya mwĩrĩ wake, no mũndũ ũrĩa ũhũũraga ũmaraya-rĩ, nĩ mwĩrĩ wake mwene ehagĩria. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 2:21">Joh 2:21</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 14:7">Arom 14:7</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 14:8">8</ref></char></note>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ mĩĩrĩ yanyu nĩ hekarũ ya Roho Mũtheru ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wanyu, ũrĩa mwaheirwo nĩ Ngai? Inyuĩ mũtirĩ anyu inyuĩ ene; <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">6:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="REV 5:9">Kũg 5:9</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 1:20">Afil 1:20</ref></char></note>inyuĩ mwagũrirwo na thogora. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, tĩĩithagiai Ngai na mĩĩrĩ yanyu.</para>
  <chapter number="7" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ũhoro wa Kũhikania</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 7:8">1Akor 7:8</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 7:26">26</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa mwanyandĩkĩire marũa nĩ ũndũ wamo, ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Nĩ wega mũndũ mũrũme kwaga kũhikania. <verse number="2" style="v"/>No tondũ wa ũrĩa ũmaraya ũingĩhĩte-rĩ, o mũndũ mũrũme nĩagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũgĩa na mũtumia wake mwene, na mũndũ-wa-nja agĩe na mũthuuri wake mwene. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 21:10">Thaam 21:10</ref></char></note>Mũthuuri nĩagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũhingagĩria mũtumia wake bata wake wa kĩhiko, o nake mũtumia ahingagĩrie mũthuuriwe bata wake. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Mũtumia ndangĩĩathĩra mwĩrĩ wake mwene, tondũ nĩ wake na mũthuuriwe. Ũguo no taguo mũthuuri atangĩĩathĩra mwĩrĩ wake mwene, tondũ nĩ wake na mũtumia wake. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 19:15">Thaam 19:15</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 21:4">1Sam 21:4</ref>, <ref loc="1SA 21:5">5</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 4:10">Math 4:10</ref></char></note>Tigagai kũimana, o tiga rĩrĩa mũngĩkorwo mũiguanĩire, naguo gũkorwo nĩ kwa ihinda, nĩgeetha mũgĩĩage na ihinda rĩa kũhooya. Thuutha ũcio no mũcooke hamwe rĩngĩ, nĩguo Shaitani ndakamũgerie tondũ wanyu kũremwo kwĩgirĩrĩria. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 8:8">2Akor 8:8</ref></char></note>Ũhoro ũcio ndawaaria taarĩ rũũtha ngũheana, no ti gwathana ngwathana. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:5">1Akor 9:5</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 12:4">1Akor 12:4</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 12:11">11</ref></char></note>No nyende andũ othe mahaane ta ũrĩa niĩ ndariĩ. No o mũndũ aheetwo kĩheo gĩake mwene kuuma kũrĩ Ngai; mũndũ ũmwe aheetwo kĩheo gĩkĩ, na ũrĩa ũngĩ akaheo kĩrĩa kĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 7:1">1Akor 7:1</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 7:26">26</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa andũ arĩa matahikanĩtie na atumia a ndigwa, nguuga ũũ: Nĩ wega maikare o ũguo matahikanĩtie, o ta ũrĩa niĩ ndariĩ. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 5:14">1Tim 5:14</ref></char></note>No angĩkorwo matingĩhota kwĩgirĩrĩria-rĩ, nĩmahike na mahikanie, tondũ nĩ kaba kũhikania gũkĩra gũikara makĩhĩĩahĩaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAL 2:14-16">Mal 2:14-16</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 16:18">Luk 16:18</ref></char>
    </note>Kũrĩ andũ arĩa mahikĩte na makahikania-rĩ, ngwathana ũũ, no ti niĩ, nĩ Mwathani ũgwathana: Mũtumia ndakanatigane na mũthuuriwe. <verse number="11" style="v"/>No aangĩka ũguo-rĩ, nĩagĩikare atarĩ mũhiku, kana akorwo ti ũguo, acookerere mũthuuriwe. Ningĩ mũthuuri ndakanaingate mũtumia wake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa acio angĩ nguuga ũũ, no nĩ niĩ ndĩroiga, ti Mwathani: Angĩkorwo mũrũ wa Ithe witũ arĩ na mũtumia ũtetĩkĩtie, na mũtumia ũcio etĩkĩre matũũranie-rĩ, nĩatige kũmũingata. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nake mũtumia angĩkorwo arĩ na mũthuuri ũtetĩkĩtie, na mũthuuri ũcio etĩkĩre matũũranie-rĩ, nĩatige kũmũingata. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAL 2:15">Mal 2:15</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũthuuri ũrĩa ũtetĩkĩtie nĩatheretio nĩ ũndũ wa mũtumia wake, nake mũtumia ũrĩa ũtarĩ mwĩtĩkia nĩatheretio nĩ ũndũ wa mũthuuri wake mwĩtĩkia. Kũngĩaga gũtuĩka ũguo-rĩ, ciana cianyu no ituĩke ti theru, no ũrĩa kũrĩ rĩu nĩ atĩ nĩ theru.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 14:19">Arom 14:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, mũndũ ũcio ũtetĩkĩtie angĩthiĩ-rĩ, nĩarekwo athiĩ. Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ mũrũme, kana mũndũ-wa-nja ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩtie ti muohe nĩ ũhoro ta ũcio; Ngai atwĩtĩte tũtũũranagie na thayũ. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:4">Arom 11:4</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 3:1">1Pet 3:1</ref></char></note>Wee mũtumia-rĩ, ũũĩ atĩa kana nĩwe ũkaahonokia mũthuuri waku? O na wee mũthuuri-rĩ, ũũĩ atĩa kana nĩwe ũkaahonokia mũtumia waku?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:3">Arom 12:3</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 4:17">1Akor 4:17</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, mũndũ o mũndũ nĩaikare mũtũũrĩre ũrĩa Mwathani aamũgaĩire, o ũrĩa Ngai aamwĩtĩire. Ũyũ nĩguo watho ũrĩa ngwatha makanitha mothe. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 15:1">Atũm 15:1</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 15:2">2</ref></char></note>Mũndũ angĩkorwo eetirwo arĩ mũruu-rĩ, nĩatige gũikara ta atarĩ mũruu. Mũndũ ũrĩa ũtaarĩ mũruu rĩrĩa eetirwo nĩatige kũrua. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 5:6">Agal 5:6</ref></char></note>Kũrua gũtirĩ bata; o na kwaga kũrua gũtirĩ bata. Ũndũ ũrĩa ũrĩ bata nĩ kũmenyerera maathani ma Ngai. <verse number="20" style="v"/>O mũndũ nĩaikarage o ũrĩa aatariĩ rĩrĩa Ngai aamwĩtire. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Wee warĩ ngombo rĩrĩa wetirwo? Ũndũ ũcio ndũgagũtange, no korwo wahota kuona njĩra ya kuuma ũkombo-inĩ-rĩ, gerera yo. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:32">Joh 8:32</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 8:36">36</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 6:22">Arom 6:22</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ ũrĩa warĩ ngombo rĩrĩa Mwathani aamwĩtire-rĩ, ũcio nĩ mũndũ wa Mwathani ũtarĩ ngombo; ningĩ no taguo, ũrĩa warĩ mũndũ muohore rĩrĩa Mwathani aamwĩtire-rĩ, ũcio nĩ ngombo ya Kristũ. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 6:20">1Akor 6:20</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ mwagũrirwo goro; mũtigatuĩke ngombo cia andũ. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, o ũndũ ũrĩa mũndũ eehokeirwo nĩ Ngai-rĩ, nĩaikarage o ũguo ũndũ ũcio Ngai aamwĩtĩire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:13">1Tim 1:13</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 1:16">16</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩu-rĩ, ũhoro wĩgiĩ airĩtu nĩ ũyũ: Ndirĩ na watho uumĩte kũrĩ Mwathani, no nĩngũheana itua rĩakwa ta mũndũ mwĩhokeku nĩ ũndũ wa kũiguĩrwo tha nĩ Mwathani. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 7:1">1Akor 7:1</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 7:8">8</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa mathĩĩna ma mahinda maya-rĩ, nguona arĩ wega mũikarage o ũrĩa mũndũ atariĩ. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Wee nĩũhikanĩtie? Ndũkaingate mũtumia waku. Wee nawe hihi ndũhikanĩtie? Tiga kũhikania. <verse number="28" style="v"/>No ũngĩhikania-rĩ, wee ndwĩhĩtie; o na mũirĩtu angĩhika-rĩ, o nake ndehĩtie. No andũ arĩa marahika kana makahikania-rĩ, nĩmarĩonaga mathĩĩna maingĩ mũtũũrĩre-inĩ ũyũ, na nĩmo ndĩrenda kũmũrigĩrĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 13:11">Arom 13:11</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 13:12">12</ref></char>
    </note>Ũndũ ũrĩa ndĩrenda kuuga, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, nĩ atĩ ihinda nĩ inini. Kuuma rĩu andũ arĩa marĩ na atumia nĩ kwagĩrĩire maikarage ta matarĩ nao; <verse number="30" style="v"/>arĩa maracakaya nĩmaikarage ta mataracakaya; nao arĩa makenete nĩmaikarage ta matakenete; o na arĩa mekũgũra indo, nĩmaikarage ta matarĩ kĩndũ marĩ. <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 12:27">Ahib 12:27</ref></char></note>nao arĩa mahũthagĩra indo cia thĩ ĩno, nĩmaikarage ta matohanĩtio nacio. Nĩgũkorwo ũrĩa thĩ ĩno ĩhaana rĩu-rĩ, nĩgũthira ĩrathira.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:32 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 5:5">1Tim 5:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Niĩ ingĩenda inyuĩ mũikarage mũtegwĩtanga. Mũndũ ũrĩa ũtahikanĩtie etangaga na maũndũ ma Mwathani, na eciiragia o ũrĩa angĩkenia Mwathani. <verse number="33" style="v"/>No mũndũ ũrĩa ũhikanĩtie etangaga na maũndũ ma gũkũ thĩ, na eciiragia o ũrĩa angĩkenia mũtumia wake, <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 2:37">Luk 2:37</ref></char></note>naguo wendi wa ngoro yake nĩmũgayũkanu. Mũndũ-wa-nja ũtarĩ mũhiku kana mũirĩtu etangaga na maũndũ ma Mwathani: Muoroto wake nĩ kwĩheana harĩ Mwathani mwĩrĩ na roho. No mũtumia mũhiku etangaga na maũndũ ma thĩ ĩno, na eciiragia o ũrĩa angĩkenia mũthuuriwe. <verse number="35" style="v"/>Ndĩramwarĩria maũndũ maya nĩgeetha mũgunĩke, ti atĩ nĩguo ndĩmũrigĩrĩrie, no nĩgeetha mũikarage na mĩthiĩre ĩrĩa yagĩrĩire, mwĩheanĩte biũ harĩ Mwathani mũtekũguucĩrĩrio nĩ maũndũ mangĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe angĩona atĩ nĩarahĩtĩria mũirĩtu ũrĩa orĩtie, nake mũirĩtu ũcio akorwo matukũ make ma ũirĩtu wake nĩmarahĩtũka-rĩ, mũndũ ũcio angĩigua nĩagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũhikania-rĩ, nĩeke o ũguo ekwenda. Ti kwĩhia ekwĩhia. Nĩmagĩrĩirwo mahikanie. <verse number="37" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, ũrĩa ũtuĩte na ngoro yake atekũringĩrĩrio, no nĩwe mwene wĩyendeire, na agatua itua atĩ ndekũhikia mũirĩtu ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ ũcio o nake nĩekĩte ũrĩa kwagĩrĩire. <verse number="38" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">7:38 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 13:4">Ahib 13:4</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ ũrĩa ũhikagia mũirĩtu ũrĩa orĩtie nĩekaga ũrĩa kwagĩrĩire, no ũrĩa ũngĩaga kũmũhikia nĩekaga wega makĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">7:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 7:2">Arom 7:2</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 7:3">3</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 6:14">2Akor 6:14</ref></char>
    </note>Mũtumia nĩohanĩtio na mũthuuriwe rĩrĩa rĩothe mũthuuriwe arĩ muoyo. No mũthuuriwe angĩkua, nĩmuohore na no ahikĩre mũndũ o ũrĩa angĩenda, no mũndũ ũcio no nginya akorwo nĩetĩkĩtie Mwathani. <verse number="40" style="v"/>No itua rĩakwa nĩ atĩrĩ, mũtumia ũcio angĩaga kũhika rĩngĩ, no akorwo arĩ na gĩkeno makĩria. Na ngwĩciiria atĩ niĩ o na niĩ ndĩ na Roho wa Ngai.</para>
  <chapter number="8" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Irio Irutĩirwo Mĩhianano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 15:20">Atũm 15:20</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 15:14">Arom 15:14</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ũhoro wa irio iria ikoragwo irutĩirwo mĩhianano-rĩ, nĩtũũĩ atĩ ithuothe tũrĩ na ũmenyo ũhoro-inĩ ũcio. Ũmenyo nĩũtũmaga mũndũ etũũgĩrie, no wendo nĩ gwaka wakaga. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 13:8">1Akor 13:8</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:4">1Tim 6:4</ref></char></note>Mũndũ ũrĩa wĩciiragia atĩ nĩoĩ ũndũ-rĩ, ndooĩ ũndũ ũcio wega ta ũrĩa aagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũũmenya. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 4:9">Agal 4:9</ref></char></note>No mũndũ ũrĩa wendete Ngai, ũcio nĩwe ũũĩo nĩ Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 14:15">Atũm 14:15</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 6:4">Gũcook 6:4</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ha ũhoro ũkoniĩ kũrĩa irio iria irutĩirwo mĩhianano-rĩ, nĩtũũĩ atĩ gũkũ thĩ mũhianano nĩ kĩndũ gĩa tũhũ, na atĩ gũtirĩ Ngai ũngĩ tiga o ũrĩa ũmwe. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Tondũ o na kũngĩkorwo nĩ kũrĩ indo ciĩtagwo ngai, irĩ kũũrĩa igũrũ kana irĩ gũkũ thĩ-rĩ, amu ti-itherũ nĩ kũrĩ na “ngai” nyingĩ na “aathani” aingĩ, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAL 2:10">Mal 2:10</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 11:36">Arom 11:36</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:5">Aef 4:5</ref></char></note>no harĩ ithuĩ-rĩ, Ngai no ũmwe, na nĩwe Ithe witũ, na indo ciothe cioimire kũrĩ we na tũtũũraga muoyo nĩ ũndũ wake; na kũrĩ na Mwathani o ũmwe, nake nĩwe Jesũ Kristũ, o we ũrĩa indo ciothe ciagĩire nĩ ũndũ wake, na nowe ũtũtũũragia muoyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 14:14">Arom 14:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No ti andũ othe mooĩ ũguo. Andũ amwe nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa matũũrĩte mamenyerete mĩhianano, o na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mekũrĩa irio ta icio meciiragia atĩ nĩirutĩirwo mũhianano, na tondũ thamiri ciao itirĩ hinya-rĩ, makanyiitwo nĩ thaahu. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 14:17">Arom 14:17</ref></char></note>No irio iria tũrĩĩaga itingĩtũma tũkuhĩrĩrie Ngai; tũtingĩthũkio nĩ kwaga gũcirĩa, na tũtingĩagĩrio nĩgũcirĩa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">8:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 5:13">Agal 5:13</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 14:1">Arom 14:1</ref></char>
    </note>O na kũrĩ ũguo-rĩ, menyererai atĩ wĩyathi ũcio wanyu ndũgatuĩke mũhĩnga kũrĩ arĩa matarĩ na hinya. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ o wothe ũrĩ na thamiri ĩtarĩ na hinya, angĩmuona inyuĩ mũrĩ na ũmenyo ũyũ mũkĩrĩĩra irio thĩinĩ wa hekarũ ya mũhianano-rĩ, githĩ ndangĩũmĩrĩria arĩe kĩrĩa kĩrutĩirwo mĩhianano? <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">8:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 14:15">Arom 14:15</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 14:20">20</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ ũcio thamiri yake ĩtarĩ na hinya, o ũcio Kristũ aakuĩrĩire-rĩ, agathũkio nĩ ũmenyo wanyu. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwehĩria ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ na njĩra ĩyo, na mũgatiihia thamiri ciao icio itarĩ hinya-rĩ, nĩ Kristũ mwehĩria. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, angĩkorwo kĩrĩa ndĩrarĩa no gĩtũme mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ agwe mehia-inĩ-rĩ, ndikĩagĩrĩirwo nĩ kũrĩa nyama rĩngĩ, nĩguo ndigatũme agwe.</para>
  <chapter number="9" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Maũndũ marĩa Maagĩrĩire Mũtũmwo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 12:12">2Akor 12:12</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 3:6">1Akor 3:6</ref></char>
    </note>Githĩ niĩ ndirĩ na wĩyathi? Githĩ niĩ ndirĩ mũtũmwo? Githĩ niĩ ndionire Jesũ Mwathani witũ? Anga inyuĩ mũtirĩ maciaro ma wĩra wakwa thĩinĩ wa Mwathani? <verse number="2" style="v"/>O na angĩkorwo andũ arĩa angĩ mationaga ta ndĩ mũtũmwo-rĩ, ti-itherũ niĩ harĩ inyuĩ ndĩ mũtũmwo! Nĩgũkorwo nĩ inyuĩ kĩmenyithia kĩa ũtũmwo wakwa thĩinĩ wa Mwathani.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>Gwĩtetera gwakwa harĩ arĩa manjiirithagia nĩ gũkũ: <verse number="4" style="v"/>Githĩ ithuĩ tũtirĩ na kĩhooto gĩa kũrĩa na kũnyua? <verse number="5" style="v"/>Githĩ ithuĩ tũtirĩ na kĩhooto kĩa mũndũ gũtwarana rũgendo-inĩ na mũtumia wake mwĩtĩkia, o ta ũrĩa atũmwo arĩa angĩ, na ariũ a nyina na Mwathani, o na Kefa mekaga? <verse number="6" style="v"/>Kana no niĩ tũrĩ na Baranaba arĩ o nginya tũrutage wĩra nĩguo tuone ũteithio witũ?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 27:18">Thim 27:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nũũ ũtungataga ta mũthigari na akeerĩha na indo ciake we mwene? Nĩ mũndũ ũrĩkũ ũhaandaga mũgũnda wa mĩthabibũ na ndarĩe thabibũ cia mũgũnda ũcio? Ningĩ-rĩ, nĩ kũrĩ mũndũ ũrĩithagia rũũru na ndanyue iria rĩa rũũru rũu? <verse number="8" style="v"/>Ndĩraaria ũhoro ũyũ ndĩ na meciiria ma ũ-mũndũ tu? Githĩ Watho o naguo nduugĩte o ũguo? <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 25:1-4">Gũcook 25:1-4</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 5:18">1Tim 5:18</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 12:10">Thim 12:10</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo watho-inĩ wa Musa atĩrĩ, “Ndũkanohe ndegwa kanua hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ĩkũranga ngano ĩkĩmĩhũũra.” Ngai akiuga ũguo-rĩ, nĩ ndegwa aracaaĩra? <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 11:25">Thim 11:25</ref></char></note>Ti-itherũ oigaga ũguo nĩ ũndũ witũ, githĩ tiguo? Ĩĩ-ni, ũndũ ũyũ waandĩkirũo nĩ ũndũ witũ, tondũ rĩrĩa mũrĩmi ekũrĩma, nake mũhũũri ngano amĩhũũrage-rĩ, nĩ kwagĩrĩire mekage ũguo marĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro atĩ nĩmakagayana magetha. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:27">Arom 15:27</ref></char></note>Tũngĩkorwo ithuĩ nĩtũhaandĩte mbeũ ya kĩĩroho thĩinĩ wanyu-rĩ, kaĩ akĩrĩ ũndũ mũnene ithuĩ tũngĩgetha indo cia gũtũũria mwĩrĩ kuuma kũrĩ inyuĩ? <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:7-12">2Akor 11:7-12</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo andũ angĩ marĩ na kĩhooto gĩa gũteithio nĩ inyuĩ-rĩ, ithuĩ githĩ tũtikĩagĩrĩirwo nĩgũteithio makĩria?</para>
  <para style="p">No ithuĩ tũtiahũthĩrire kĩhooto kĩu. Handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, nĩ gũkirĩrĩria tũkiragĩrĩria ũndũ o wothe nĩguo tũtikae kũhĩngĩca Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega wa Kristũ. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 6:16">Alaw 6:16</ref>, <ref loc="LEV 6:26">26</ref></char></note>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ andũ arĩa marutaga wĩra thĩinĩ wa hekarũ marutaga irio ciao kuuma kũu hekarũ, nao arĩa matungataga kĩgongona-inĩ magayanaga kĩrĩa kĩrutĩtwo kĩgongona-inĩ? <verse number="14" style="v"/>O ta ũguo-rĩ, Mwathani nĩathanĩte atĩ arĩa mahunjagia Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega nĩmagĩrĩirwo kuonaga gĩa kũmatũũria kuuma kũrĩ Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 18:3">Atũm 18:3</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 11:9">2Akor 11:9</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 11:10">10</ref></char>
    </note>No niĩ ndirĩ ndaahũthĩra kĩhooto o na kĩmwe gĩa cio. Ningĩ ndiraandĩka ũhoro ũyũ ndĩ na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro atĩ nĩmũkũnjĩka maũndũ ta macio. Nĩ kaba ngue gũkĩra mũndũ o naũ agirie ndĩĩrahĩre ũndũ ũcio. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:14">Arom 1:14</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, ndingĩhota kwĩraha rĩrĩa ngũhunjia Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega, nĩgũkorwo nĩhatagĩrĩrio mũno ndĩũhunjie. Na niĩ ingĩaga kũhunjia Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega kaĩ ndagĩa na haaro-ĩ! <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 3:8">1Akor 3:8</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 3:14">14</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 2:7">Agal 2:7</ref></char></note>Ingĩhunjia nĩ ũndũ wa kwĩyendera-rĩ, ndaheo mũcaara; no angĩkorwo ti na ũndũ wa kwĩyendera-rĩ, niĩ no kũhingia ndĩrahingia ũndũ ũrĩa ndĩhokeirwo. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:7">2Akor 11:7</ref></char></note>Hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, mũcaara wakwa ũkĩrĩ kĩ? Nĩ atĩrĩ: Atĩ harĩ ũhoro wa kũhunjia Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega-rĩ, hunjagie tũhũ itekũrĩhwo, na nĩ ũndũ ũcio njage gwĩtagia kĩhooto gĩakwa rĩrĩa ngũhunjia Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">9:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 5:13">Agal 5:13</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 18:15">Math 18:15</ref></char>
    </note>O na gũtuĩka ndĩ muohore na ndirĩ ngombo ya mũndũ-rĩ, niĩ ndĩĩtuaga ngombo ya o mũndũ wothe, nĩguo nguucĩrĩrie andũ aingĩ o ta ũrĩa kwahoteka. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 6:3">Atũm 6:3</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 2:12">Arom 2:12</ref></char></note>Kũrĩ Ayahudi ndaatuĩkire ta Mũyahudi nĩguo nguucagĩrĩrie Ayahudi. Na kũrĩ arĩa marĩ rungu rwa watho-rĩ, ndaatuĩkire ta mũndũ ũrĩ rungu rwa watho, o na gũtuĩka niĩ mwene ndirĩ rungu rwa watho, nĩguo nguucagĩrĩrie arĩa marĩ rungu rwa watho. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 2:12">Arom 2:12</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 2:14">14</ref></char></note>Kũrĩ arĩa matarĩ watho-inĩ-rĩ, ndaatuĩkire ta mũndũ ũtarĩ watho-inĩ ũcio, o na gũtuĩka ndirĩ muohore kuuma kũrĩ watho wa Ngai, no ndĩ watho-inĩ wa Kristũ, nĩguo nguucagĩrĩrie arĩa matarĩ watho-inĩ ũcio. <verse number="22" style="v"/>Kũrĩ arĩa matarĩ hinya-rĩ, ndaatuĩkire ta itarĩ hinya nĩguo nguucagĩrĩrie arĩa matarĩ hinya. Nduĩkĩte maũndũ mothe kũrĩ andũ othe nĩgeetha kũngĩhoteka na njĩra ciothe ngerie kũhonokia amwe ao. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Njĩkaga maũndũ maya mothe nĩ ũndũ wa Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega, nĩgeetha ngaagaĩrwo irathimo ciaguo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Kaĩ inyuĩ mũtooĩ atĩ andũ arĩa mahĩtahĩtanaga ihenya-inĩ mahanyũkaga othe, no rĩrĩ, no ũmwe wao ũheagwo kĩheo? Kĩhanyũkei na njĩra ĩrĩa ĩngĩtũma mũkaaheo kĩheo.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9:24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Andũ a Korinitho nĩmamenyerete mahenya mathako-inĩ marĩa moĩkaine ta Isimithiani. Mũhootani aaheagwo ihũa rĩa gĩthiũrũrĩ.</char></note> <verse number="25" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũhĩtahĩtanaga thĩinĩ wa mathako-rĩ, ehataga na akemenyeria maũndũ-inĩ mothe hatarĩ itherũ. Mekaga ũguo nĩguo maheo thũmbĩ ĩtarĩ ya gũtũũra; no ithuĩ twĩkaga ũguo nĩguo tũkaaheo thũmbĩ ya gũtũũra nginya tene. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, niĩ ndihanyũkaga ta mũndũ ũtooĩ gĩtũmi gĩa kũhanyũka; na ndirũaga ta mũndũ ũgũikia ngundi ciake o ũguo tũhũ. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">9:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:13">Arom 8:13</ref></char></note>Aca, nĩ mwĩrĩ wakwa hũũraga ngaũtua ngombo yakwa, nĩgeetha ndaarĩkia kũhunjĩria andũ arĩa angĩ-rĩ, niĩ mwene ndikanatuĩke wa kũregwo nyimwo kĩheo.</para>
  <chapter number="10" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ũrutani kuuma Mũtũũrĩre wa Isiraeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EXO 13:21">Thaam 13:21</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 14:22">Thaam 14:22</ref>, <ref loc="EXO 14:29">29</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 6:3">Arom 6:3</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ndikwenda mũkorwo mũtooĩ ũndũ ũyũ, atĩ maithe maitũ ma tene othe maatongoragio nĩ itu, na atĩ othe nĩmaringire iria. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Othe nĩmabatithirio matuĩke andũ a Musa marĩ rungu rwa itu rĩu, o na marĩ iria-inĩ rĩu. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 6:31">Joh 6:31</ref></char></note>Na othe maarĩĩaga irio o imwe cia kĩĩroho, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 17:6">Thaam 17:6</ref></char></note>na maanyuuaga maaĩ o mamwe ma kĩĩroho; nĩgũkorwo maanyuire kuuma rwaro-inĩ rwa ihiga rwa kĩĩroho rũrĩa rwatwaranaga nao, naruo rwaro rũu rwarĩ Kristũ. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 14:29">Ndar 14:29</ref></char></note>O na kũrĩ ũguo-rĩ, aingĩ ao matiigana gũkenia Ngai; nacio ciimba ciao ikĩhurunjwo werũ-inĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, maũndũ macio meekĩkire marĩ ta cionereria, nĩgeetha ngoro ciitũ itikerirĩrie gwĩka maũndũ mooru ta macio meekire. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 32:4-19">Thaam 32:4-19</ref></char></note>Mũtigatuĩke ahooi mĩhianano, ta ũrĩa amwe ao maatariĩ; o ta ũrĩa kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: “Andũ acio magĩikara thĩ kũrĩa na kũnyua, magĩcooka magĩũkĩra kũina na gwĩkenia.” <verse number="8" style="v"/>Ningĩ tũtikahũũre ũmaraya, ta ũrĩa amwe ao meekire, nao magĩkua andũ ngiri mĩrongo ĩĩrĩ na ithatũ mũthenya ũmwe. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 21:5">Ndar 21:5</ref>, <ref loc="NUM 21:6">6</ref></char></note>O na ningĩ tũtikanagerie Mwathani, ta ũrĩa amwe ao meekire, nao makĩniinwo nĩ nyoka. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 16:49">Ndar 16:49</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 12:23">Thaam 12:23</ref></char></note>Na mũtikae gũteta, ta ũrĩa amwe ao meekire, nao makĩũragwo nĩ mũraika ũrĩa mũniinani.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 4:24">Arom 4:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Maũndũ macio meekĩkire kũrĩ o marĩ cionereria, na makĩandĩkwo marĩ ma gũtũkaania, ithuĩ tũkinyĩrĩirwo nĩ kũhingio kwa mahinda. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:20">Arom 11:20</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ũngĩĩra nĩũrũgamĩte wega-rĩ, menyerera ndũkae kũgũa! <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 2:9">2Pet 2:9</ref></char></note>Mũtirĩ mwagerio na magerio mangĩ tiga o marĩa makoraga andũ. Nake Ngai nĩmwĩhokeku; ndangĩtĩkĩra mũgerio na magerio marĩa mũtangĩhota gwĩtiiria. No rĩrĩa mũkũgerio-rĩ, nĩarĩmuonagĩrĩria njĩra ya kũũrĩra nĩguo mũhotage gwĩtiiria magerio macio.</para>
  <para style="s1">Maruga ma Mĩhianano, na Gĩathĩ kĩa Mwathani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 6:9">Ahib 6:9</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, arata akwa endwa, ũragĩrai ũhoro wa kũhooya mĩhianano. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Ndĩraarĩria andũ oogĩ; mwĩkũũranĩrei ũrĩa ndĩroiga. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 14:19">Math 14:19</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 26:26-28">Math 26:26-28</ref></char></note>Gĩkombe gĩa gũcookia ngaatho kĩrĩa tũcookagia ngaatho nĩ ũndũ wakĩo-rĩ, githĩ ti kũgwatanĩra thakame ya Kristũ?<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">10:16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Gĩkombe gĩa gũcookia ngaatho kĩarĩ kĩmwe gĩa ikombe iria Ayahudi maanyuuaga hĩndĩ ya Bathaka.</char></note> Na githĩ mũgate ũrĩa twenyũraga ti kũgwatanĩra mwĩrĩ wa Kristũ? <verse number="17" style="v"/>Na tondũ mũgate ũcio nĩ ũmwe-rĩ, ithuĩ, o na tũrĩ aingĩ, tũrĩ o mwĩrĩ ũmwe, nĩgũkorwo ithuĩ othe tũrĩĩaga mũgate o ũcio ũmwe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ta mwĩcũraniei ũhoro wa andũ a Isiraeli: Arĩa marĩĩaga irio cia igongona-rĩ, githĩ matigwatanagĩra kĩgongona kĩu? <verse number="19" style="v"/>Ndĩrenda kuuga atĩa? Atĩ kĩrĩa kĩrutĩirwo mũhianano nĩ kĩndũ kũrĩ, kana atĩ mũhianano guo mwene nĩ kĩndũ kũrĩ? <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 32:17">Gũcook 32:17</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 106:37">Thab 106:37</ref></char></note>Aca! Ũrĩa ndĩroiga nĩ atĩ magongona ma andũ arĩa matarĩ na ũngai marutagĩrwo ndaimono, na ti Ngai, na ndikwenda mũgĩe ngwatanĩro na ndaimono. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 6:15">2Akor 6:15</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 6:16">16</ref></char></note>Mũtingĩhota kũnyuĩra gĩkombe kĩa Mwathani, na mũnyuĩre gĩkombe kĩa ndaimono o nakĩo; mũtingĩhota kũgwatanĩra metha-inĩ ya Mwathani, na mũgwatanĩre metha-inĩ ya ndaimono. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 32:16">Gũcook 32:16</ref>, <ref loc="DEU 32:21">21</ref>; <ref loc="ECC 6:10">Koh 6:10</ref></char></note>Kaĩ tũrageria kwarahũra ũiru wa Mwathani? Kaĩ tũrĩ na hinya kũmũkĩra?</para>
  <para style="s1">Wĩyathi wa Mũndũ ũrĩa Wĩtĩkĩtie</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 6:12">1Akor 6:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Niĩ ndirigĩrĩirio gwĩka ũndũ,” no ti ũndũ o wothe ũrĩ na kĩguni. “Niĩ ndirigĩrĩirio gwĩka ũndũ,” no ti ũndũ o wothe ũrĩ na uumithio. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:1">Arom 15:1</ref>, <ref loc="ROM 15:2">2</ref></char></note>Gũtirĩ mũndũ wagĩrĩirwo nĩgũcaragia maũndũ ma kwĩguna we mwene, no nĩacaragie maũndũ ma kũguna andũ arĩa angĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>Rĩĩagai kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩendagio thoko-inĩ ya nyama mũtekwĩyũria ciũria nĩ ũndũ wa mwĩcuuko wa thamiri, <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 41:11">Ayub 41:11</ref></char></note>nĩgũkorwo, “Thĩ nĩ ya Mwathani, na kĩrĩa gĩothe kĩrĩ thĩinĩ wayo.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 10:7">Luk 10:7</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mũndũ ũtarĩ mwĩtĩkia angĩmwĩta mũkarĩe irio gwake, na inyuĩ mũkorwo nĩ mũkwenda gũthiĩ-rĩ, rĩa irio ciothe iria mũngĩheo mũtekwĩyũria ciũria cia mwĩcuuko wa thamiri. <verse number="28" style="v"/>No mũndũ angĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Irio ici irutĩtwo irĩ igongona,” mũtigacirĩe, nĩ ũndũ wa mũndũ ũcio wamwĩra ũguo, o na nĩ ũndũ wa mwĩcuuko wa thamiri; <verse number="29" style="v"/>ngiuga ũguo ti thamiri yaku ndagweta, no nĩ thamiri ya mũndũ ũcio ũngĩ. Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, wĩyathi wakwa ũgũciirithio nĩkĩ nĩ ũndũ wa thamiri ya mũndũ ũngĩ? <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 14:6">Arom 14:6</ref></char></note>Ingĩrĩanĩra irio na andũ angĩ ndĩ na ngaatho-rĩ, nĩ kĩĩ gĩgũtũma njambio nĩ ũndũ wa kĩndũ kĩu njokeirie Ngai ngaatho nĩ ũndũ wakĩo?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">10:31 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 3:17">Akol 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 4:11">1Pet 4:11</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, rĩrĩa mũkũrĩa kana rĩrĩa mũkũnyua, o na kana mũgĩĩka ũndũ o wothe-rĩ, wĩkagei nĩ ũndũ wa kwenda kũgoocithia Ngai. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 6:3">2Akor 6:3</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 20:28">Atũm 20:28</ref></char></note>Tigai gwĩka ũndũ ũngĩhĩngithia mũndũ, arĩ Mũyahudi, kana arĩ Mũyunani, o na kana ũhĩngithie kanitha wa Ngai, <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">10:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:2">Arom 15:2</ref></char></note>o ta ũrĩa niĩ ngeragia gũkenia andũ othe na njĩra o yothe. Nĩgũkorwo ndicaragia ũndũ wa kwĩguna niĩ mwene, no njaragia ũrĩa ingĩguna andũ aingĩ, nĩguo mahonoke.</para>
  <chapter number="11" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Mwĩgerekaniei na niĩ, ta ũrĩa ndĩgerekanagia na Kristũ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ũndũ ũrĩa Wagĩrĩire Hĩndĩ ya Mahooya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 4:17">1Akor 4:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩngũmũgaathĩrĩria nĩ ũndũ wa kũndirikana maũndũ-inĩ mothe, na nĩ ũndũ wa gũtũũra mũrũmĩtie morutani macio, o ta ũrĩa ndaamũrutire.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 3:16">Kĩam 3:16</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 5:23">Aef 5:23</ref></char>
    </note>Rĩu-rĩ, nĩngwenda mũmenye atĩ mũtwe wa mũndũ mũrũme o wothe nĩ Kristũ, na mũtwe wa mũndũ-wa-nja nĩ mũndũ mũrũme, na mũtwe wa Kristũ nĩ Ngai. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Mũndũ mũrũme o wothe ũrĩa ũhooyaga kana akaratha ehumbĩrĩte mũtwe-rĩ, nĩ mũtwe wake aconorithagia. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 21:9">Atũm 21:9</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 21:12">Gũcook 21:12</ref></char></note>Nake mũndũ-wa-nja o wothe ũrĩa ũhooyaga kana akaratha atahumbĩrĩte mũtwe wake-rĩ, nĩ mũtwe wake aconorithagia, tondũ ũguo no ũndũ ũmwe na kwenjwo. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo mũndũ-wa-nja ndekũhumbĩra mũtwe wake-rĩ, nĩakĩenje njuĩrĩ yake; na angĩkorwo kũrengarenga njuĩrĩ kana kwenjwo nĩ ũndũ wa gũconora mũndũ-wa-nja-rĩ, nĩakĩĩhumbĩre mũtwe. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 1:26">Kĩam 1:26</ref></char></note>Mũndũ mũrũme ndaagĩrĩirwo nĩkũhumbĩra mũtwe wake, kuona atĩ nĩwe mũhianĩre wa Ngai, na nĩ riiri wa Ngai; no mũndũ-wa-nja nĩwe riiri wa mũndũ mũrũme. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 2:21-23">Kĩam 2:21-23</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ mũrũme ndoimire harĩ mũndũ-wa-nja, no nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja woimire harĩ mũndũ mũrũme. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 2:18">Kĩam 2:18</ref></char></note>Mũndũ mũrũme-rĩ, tiwe wombirwo nĩ ũndũ wa mũndũ-wa-nja, no nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja wombirwo nĩ ũndũ wa mũndũ mũrũme. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ wa gĩtũmi gĩkĩ-rĩ, mũndũ-wa-nja agĩrĩirwo nĩgũkorwo na rũũri mũtwe rwa kuonania atĩ nĩ wa gwathwo nĩ ũndũ wa araika.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>No ningĩ-rĩ, thĩinĩ wa Mwathani, mũndũ-wa-nja ndeiganĩtie mũndũ mũrũme atarĩ ho, nake mũndũ-mũrũme ndeiganĩtie mũndũ-wa-nja atarĩ ho. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:36">Arom 11:36</ref></char></note>O ta ũrĩa mũndũ-wa-nja oimire harĩ mũndũ mũrũme-rĩ, no taguo mũndũ-mũrũme aciaragwo nĩ mũndũ-wa-nja. No rĩrĩ, indo ciothe ciumaga kũrĩ Ngai. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Ta tuai arĩ inyuĩ: Nĩ kwagĩrĩire mũndũ-wa-nja kũhooya Ngai atehumbĩrĩte mũtwe? <verse number="14" style="v"/>Kaĩ maũndũ ma ndũire matamũrutaga atĩ mũndũ-mũrũme gũkorwo arĩ na njuĩrĩ ndaaya nĩ ũndũ wa kũmũconorithia, <verse number="15" style="v"/>no mũndũ-wa-nja gũkorwo na njuĩrĩ ndaaya, ũcio nĩ riiri wake? Nĩgũkorwo aheetwo njuĩrĩ ndaaya arĩ kĩndũ gĩa kũmũhumbĩra. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 7:17">1Akor 7:17</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo kũrĩ na mũndũ ũrĩ na ngarari na ũhoro ũyũ-rĩ, nĩamenye atĩ ithuĩ tũtirĩ mũtugo ũngĩ, o na makanitha ma Ngai matirĩ mũtugo ũngĩ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Irio cia Mwathani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 11:22">1Akor 11:22</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũhoro-inĩ ũrĩa ngũmũtaarĩria rĩu-rĩ, ndirĩ na ũndũ wa kũmũgaathĩra, nĩgũkorwo kũngana kwanyu ti gwa kũmũguna no nĩ gwa kũmũthũkia. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:10-12">1Akor 1:10-12</ref></char></note>Ũndũ wa mbere, njiguaga atĩ rĩrĩa muongana ta kanitha, nĩkũgĩaga na nyamũkano gatagatĩ kanyu, na ũhoro ũcio ndingĩaga gwĩtĩkia ũmwe waguo. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:19">1Joh 2:19</ref></char></note>Hatarĩ nganja gũtingĩaga kũgĩa na ngarari gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu cia kuonania arĩa anyu metĩkĩrĩkĩte nĩ Ngai. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Rĩrĩa muongana hamwe, ti Irio cia Mwathani mũrĩĩaga, <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JUD 1:12">Jud 12</ref></char></note>nĩgũkorwo rĩrĩa mũkũrĩa, o mũndũ athiiaga na mbere kũrĩa ategweterera ũrĩa ũngĩ. Ũmwe aikaraga ahũtiĩ, nake ũrĩa ũngĩ agaikara arĩĩtwo. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:32">1Akor 10:32</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 2:6">Jak 2:6</ref></char></note>Kaĩ mũtarĩ mĩciĩ mũngĩrĩĩra na mũnyuĩre kuo? Kana nĩ kanitha wa Ngai mũnyararĩte na mũkenda gũconoraga arĩa matarĩ kĩndũ? Ngũkĩmwĩra atĩa? No ndĩkĩmũgaathĩrĩrie nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoro ũcio? Aca, ndingĩmũgaathĩrĩria!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 1:12">Agal 1:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo ũhoro ũrĩa ndaamũkĩrire kuuma kũrĩ Mwathani noguo ndaamũkinyĩirie: Mwathani Jesũ, ũtukũ ũrĩa aakunyanĩirwo, nĩooire mũgate, <verse number="24" style="v"/>na aarĩkia gũcookia ngaatho,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11:24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Warĩ mũtugo wa Ayahudi gũcookia ngaatho mbere ya kũrĩa irio.</char></note> akĩwenyũranga, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Ũyũ nĩ mwĩrĩ wakwa, ũrĩa ũheanĩtwo nĩ ũndũ wanyu; ĩkagai ũũ nĩguo mũndirikanage.” <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:16">1Akor 10:16</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 22:20">Luk 22:20</ref></char></note>Ningĩ o ũndũ ũmwe, thuutha wa kũrĩa irio, akĩoya gĩkombe, akiuga atĩrĩ, “Gĩkombe gĩkĩ nĩ kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa kĩerũ thĩinĩ wa thakame yakwa; ĩkagai ũũ, rĩrĩa rĩothe mũrĩkĩnyuuagĩra, nĩguo mũndirikanage.” <verse number="26" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo rĩrĩa rĩothe mũkũrĩa mũgate ũyũ na mũkanyuĩra gĩkombe gĩkĩ-rĩ, nĩkuumbũra mũkuumbũra gũkua kwa Mwathani o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa agooka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">11:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 10:29">Ahib 10:29</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, mũndũ o wothe ũkũrĩa mũgate ũcio kana akanyuĩra gĩkombe kĩu kĩa Mwathani ũrĩa gũtaagĩrĩire-rĩ, nĩ kwĩhia ehĩirie mwĩrĩ na thakame ya Mwathani. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 13:5">2Akor 13:5</ref></char></note>Mũndũ nĩambage gwĩtuĩria mbere ya kũrĩa mũgate ũcio na kũnyuĩra gĩkombe kĩu. <verse number="29" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũrĩĩaga na akanyua ategũkũũrana mwĩrĩ wa Mwathani, nĩ ituĩro rĩake we mwene etuagĩra. <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 9:24">Math 9:24</ref></char></note>Kĩu nĩkĩo gĩtũmĩte aingĩ anyu moorwo nĩ hinya, na marũare, na amwe anyu nĩmarĩkĩtie gũkua. <verse number="31" style="v"/>No tũngĩĩtuĩra ciira ithuĩ ene, tũtingĩtuĩka a gũciirithio. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 94:12">Thab 94:12</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 15:18-19">Joh 15:18-19</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa tũgũtuĩrwo ciira nĩ Mwathani-rĩ, nĩkũherithio tũherithagio nĩgeetha tũtikae gũtuĩrwo ciira hamwe na thĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, rĩrĩa mũnganĩte mũrĩĩanĩre-rĩ, etanagĩrĩrai. <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">11:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 4:19">1Akor 4:19</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo mũndũ nĩahũũtiĩ-rĩ, agĩrĩirwo nĩ kũrĩa irio gwake mũciĩ, nĩgeetha rĩrĩa muongana gũtikagĩe ũhoro wa gũtuĩrwo ciira.</para>
  <para style="p">Nĩngaheana ũhoro wa maũndũ macio mangĩ rĩrĩa ngooka.</para>
  <chapter number="12" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Iheo cia Roho Mũtheru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:11">Arom 1:11</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 11:25">Arom 11:25</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ha ũhoro wa iheo cia kĩĩroho-rĩ, ndikwenda mũikare mũrigĩtwo nĩguo. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:2">Aef 2:2</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 115:5">Thab 115:5</ref></char></note>Inyuĩ nĩmũũĩ atĩ hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũteetĩkĩtie Ngai, nĩmwaguucagĩrĩrio na mũkerekerio kũrĩ mĩhianano ĩtangĩaria. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 9:3">Arom 9:3</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 4:2">1Joh 4:2</ref>, <ref loc="1JN 4:3">3</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngũmwĩra atĩ, gũtirĩ mũndũ waragia ahotithĩtio nĩ Roho wa Ngai ũngiuga atĩrĩ, “Jesũ aronyiitwo nĩ kĩrumi,” na gũtirĩ mũndũ ũngĩhota kuuga atĩrĩ, “Jesũ nĩ Mwathani,” atatongoretio nĩ Roho Mũtheru.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:4-8">Arom 12:4-8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, iheo iria iheanagwo nĩ mĩthemba mĩthemba, no Roho ũrĩa ũciheanaga no ũmwe. <verse number="5" style="v"/>O na njĩra cia gũtungata nĩ mĩthemba mĩthemba, no Mwathani ũrĩa ũtungatagwo no ũmwe. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:6">Aef 4:6</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:13">Afil 2:13</ref></char></note>Ningĩ kũrĩ mĩrutĩre ya wĩra mĩthemba mĩthemba, no Ngai no ũmwe ũrĩa ũhotithagia maũndũ mothe gwĩkĩka thĩinĩ wa andũ othe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, o mũndũ nĩaheagwo ũndũ wa kuonania atĩ arĩ na Roho, naguo ũndũ ũcio nĩ wa kũguna andũ othe. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 2:6">1Akor 2:6</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 8:7">2Akor 8:7</ref></char></note>Roho ũcio nĩwe ũheaga mũndũ ũmwe ndũmĩrĩri ya ũũgĩ, na ũngĩ akaheo ũmenyo nĩ Roho o ro ũcio, <verse number="9" style="v"/>nake ũngĩ akaheo wĩtĩkio nĩ Roho o ro ũcio, na ũngĩ akaheo iheo cia kũhonania nĩ Roho o ro ũcio, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 3:5">Agal 3:5</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:11">Aef 4:11</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 4:1">1Joh 4:1</ref></char></note>nake ũngĩ akaheo hinya wa kũringa ciama, na ũngĩ akaheo ũrathi, na ũngĩ akaheo gũkũũrana maroho, na ũngĩ akaheo kwaria na thiomi mĩthemba mĩthemba, ningĩ ũngĩ akaheo ũhoti wa gũtaũra thiomi icio. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Maũndũ macio mothe nĩ wĩra wa Roho o ro ũcio ũmwe, nake agayagĩra o mũndũ o ũrĩa ekwenda.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mwĩrĩ Ũmwe ũrĩ Ciĩga Nyingĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Mwĩrĩ wa mũndũ nĩ ũmwe, o na gwatuĩka ũrĩ ciĩga nyingĩ; ningĩ o na gwatuĩka ciĩga ciaguo ciothe nĩ nyingĩ-rĩ, ciothe no mwĩrĩ o ũmwe. Ũguo noguo Kristũ atariĩ. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 3:28">Agal 3:28</ref>; <ref loc="COL 3:11">Akol 3:11</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 7:37-39">Joh 7:37-39</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ithuothe twabatithirio na Roho ũmwe tũgĩtuĩka a mwĩrĩ ũmwe, o na tũrĩ Ayahudi kana tũrĩ Ayunani, tũrĩ ngombo o na kana tũtarĩ ngombo, na ithuothe tũkĩnyuithio Roho o ro ũcio ũmwe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, mwĩrĩ ndũkoragwo na kĩĩga kĩmwe, no nĩ wa ciĩga nyingĩ. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Kũgũrũ kũngiuga atĩ, “Tondũ ti niĩ guoko-rĩ, ndirĩ wa mwĩrĩ ũyũ,” Ũndũ ũcio ndũngĩtũma gũtige gũtuĩka kĩĩga kĩa mwĩrĩ ũcio. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nakuo gũtũ kũngiuga atĩ, “Tondũ ti niĩ riitho-rĩ, ndirĩ wa mwĩrĩ ũcio,” nĩ ũndũ wa gĩtũmi kĩu gũtingĩtiga gũtuĩka kĩĩga kĩa mwĩrĩ ũcio. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Mwĩrĩ wothe ũngĩkorwo no riitho-rĩ, kũigua tũngĩiguaga na kĩ? Mwĩrĩ wothe ũngĩkorwo no gũtũ-rĩ, kũnungĩra tũngĩnungagĩra na kĩ? <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:28">1Akor 12:28</ref></char></note>No ũrĩa kũrĩ, nĩ atĩ Ngai nĩ eekĩrire ciĩga ciothe thĩinĩ wa mwĩrĩ, agĩciĩkĩra o ta ũrĩa eendaga ciikare. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Ciĩga ciothe ingĩtuĩka nĩ kĩĩga kĩmwe-rĩ, mwĩrĩ naguo ũngĩkorwo ha? <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 12:5">Arom 12:5</ref></char></note>Ũrĩa kũrĩ nĩ atĩ ciĩga nĩ nyingĩ, no mwĩrĩ nĩ ũmwe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Riitho rĩtingĩhota kwĩra guoko atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndirĩ na bata nawe!” Naguo mũtwe wĩre magũrũ atĩrĩ, “Niĩ ndirĩ na bata na inyuĩ!” <verse number="22" style="v"/>Handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, ciĩga cia mwĩrĩ iria cionekaga itarĩ hinya, nĩcio irĩ bata makĩria, <verse number="23" style="v"/>nacio ciĩga iria tuonaga ta itarĩ cia gũtĩĩo mũno-rĩ, nĩcio tũheaga gĩtĩĩo kĩa mwanya. Nacio ciĩga iria tuonaga ta itagĩrĩire kuoneka nĩimenyagĩrĩrwo mũno, <verse number="24" style="v"/>o rĩrĩa ciĩga ciitũ iria itarĩ cia kũhithwo itabataragio nĩkũmenyererwo mũno. No Ngai nĩanyiitithanĩtie ciĩga cia mwĩrĩ na agatĩĩithia makĩria ciĩga iria ciagĩte gĩtĩĩo, <verse number="25" style="v"/>nĩgeetha gũtikae kũgĩa na nyamũkano thĩinĩ wa mwĩrĩ, no nĩgeetha ciĩga ciaguo imenyanagĩrĩre o kĩĩga na kĩrĩa kĩngĩ. <verse number="26" style="v"/>Kĩĩga kĩmwe kĩngĩnyariirĩka, ciĩga iria ingĩ inyariirĩkaga hamwe nakĩo; nakĩo kĩĩga kĩmwe kĩngĩheo gĩtĩĩo-rĩ, o nacio ciĩga iria ingĩ nĩikenaga hamwe nakĩo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:27 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 1:23">Aef 1:23</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:18">Akol 1:18</ref>, <ref loc="COL 1:24">24</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 12:5">Arom 12:5</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, inyuĩ mũrĩ mwĩrĩ wa Kristũ, na o mũndũ wanyu nĩ kĩĩga kĩaguo. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:11">Aef 4:11</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 12:6-8">Arom 12:6-8</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 16:7">Mar 16:7</ref></char></note>Nakuo thĩinĩ wa kanitha, Ngai nĩathuurĩte mbere andũ amwe matuĩke atũmwo, a keerĩ anabii, a gatatũ arutani, o na ningĩ kũgĩe na aringi a ciama, o na arĩa marĩ na iheo cia kũhonania mĩrimũ, na arĩa marĩ na ũhoti wa gũteithia arĩa angĩ, na arĩa marĩ na iheo cia ũtabarĩri, na arĩa maaragia na thiomi mĩthemba mĩthemba. <verse number="29" style="v"/>Andũ othe nĩ atũmwo? Andũ othe nĩ anabii? Andũ othe nĩ arutani? Andũ othe nĩ aringi a ciama? <verse number="30" style="v"/>Andũ othe nĩmaheetwo iheo cia kũhonania? Andũ othe nĩmakĩaragia na thiomi? Andũ othe nĩmagĩtaũraga thiomi? <verse number="31" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">12:31 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 14:1">1Akor 14:1</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 14:39">39</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, mwĩriragĩriei iheo iria irĩ bata mũno.</para>
  <para style="s1">Wendani</para>
  <para style="p">Na rĩu nĩngũmuonia njĩra ĩrĩa njega makĩria.</para>
  <chapter number="13" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Atĩrĩrĩ, o na ingĩaria na thiomi cia andũ o na cia araika, no ngorwo itarĩ na wendani-rĩ, ingĩkorwo ndĩ o ta kĩndũ kĩa rũthuku kĩrĩa kĩgambaga kĩaringwo, kana o ta thaani ĩrĩa ĩhũũrithanagio ĩkagamba. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 14:2">1Akor 14:2</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 17:20">Math 17:20</ref></char></note>Ingĩkorwo ndĩ na kĩheo gĩa kũratha ũhoro, na ngorwo no hote kũmenya maũndũ mothe ma hitho na ngagĩa na ũmenyo wothe, na ingĩkorwo ndĩ na wĩtĩkio ũrĩa ũngĩhota gũthaamia irĩma, no ndirĩ na wendani-rĩ, ndirĩ bata o na hanini. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 19:8">Luk 19:8</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 3:28">Dan 3:28</ref></char></note>Ingĩheana indo ciakwa ciothe kũrĩ andũ arĩa athĩĩni, o na heane mwĩrĩ wakwa ũcinwo, no ngorwo ndirĩ na wendani-rĩ, ndingĩgunĩka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>Wendani nĩũkiranagĩrĩria, na wendani nĩũtuganaga. Ndũiguanagĩra ũiru, na ndwĩgaathaga, o na ndũrĩ mwĩtĩĩo. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:24">1Akor 10:24</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:22">Math 5:22</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 14:16-17">Ayub 14:16-17</ref></char></note>Wendani ndũrĩ rũtũrĩko, na ndũcaragia ũrĩa ũngĩĩguna, o na ndũhiũhaga kũrakara, na ndũtaraga maita marĩa ũhĩtĩirio. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TH 2:12">2Athe 2:12</ref>; <ref loc="2JN 1:4">2Joh 4</ref></char></note>Ningĩ wendani ndũkenagĩra ũũru, no nĩũkenagĩra ũhoro wa ma. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Wendani nĩũgitanagĩra hĩndĩ ciothe, na ũgetĩkia maũndũ mothe, na nĩwĩrĩgagĩrĩra hĩndĩ ciothe, o na ũkomĩrĩria hĩndĩ ciothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>Wendani ndũthiraga. No akorwo nĩ morathi, nĩmagathira; o na thiomi nĩigathira; na kũmenya maũndũ o nakuo nĩgũgathira. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 8:2">2Akor 8:2</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo tũmenyaga maũndũ o gĩcunjĩ, na tũrathaga maũndũ o gĩcunjĩ, <verse number="10" style="v"/>no hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũndũ ũrĩa mũkinyanĩru ũgooka-rĩ, ũndũ ũrĩa ũtarĩ mũkinyanĩru nĩũgaathira. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndaarĩ kaana-rĩ, ndaaragia o ta kaana, na ndeeciiragia o ta kaana, na ndaataranagia maũndũ o ta kaana. No hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndaatuĩkire mũndũ mũgima-rĩ, ngĩtigana na maũndũ ma wana. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 3:2">1Joh 3:2</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 4:9">Agal 4:9</ref></char></note>Rĩu tuonaga maũndũ na mairia, ta kuona na gĩcicio; no hĩndĩ ĩyo tũkoonaga ta andũ makĩonana ũthiũ kwa ũthiũ. Rĩu njũũĩ maũndũ o gĩcunjĩ; hĩndĩ ĩyo nĩngamenya maũndũ wega, o ta ũrĩa niĩ njũũĩo wega.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Na rĩu, maũndũ maya matatũ nĩ ma gũtũũra: wĩtĩkio, na kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro, o na wendani. No ũrĩa mũnene wamo nĩ wendani.</para>
  <chapter number="14" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Iheo cia Ũrathi na cia Thiomi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 12:31">1Akor 12:31</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:11">Aef 4:11</ref></char>
    </note>Rũmagĩrĩrai mĩthiĩre ya wendani, na mwĩrirĩrie mũno iheo cia kĩĩroho, na makĩria mwĩriragĩrie kĩheo kĩa ũheani ũhoro wa Ngai. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 16:17">Mar 16:17</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 13:2">1Akor 13:2</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mũndũ ũrĩa wothe waragia na rũthiomi-rĩ, ti andũ aaragĩria no nĩ Ngai aaragĩria. Ti-itherũ, gũtirĩ mũndũ ũtaũkagĩrwo nĩ ũrĩa aroiga; no nĩ maũndũ ma hitho aaragia na roho wake. <verse number="3" style="v"/>No mũndũ ũrĩa ũheanaga ũhoro wa Ngai aaragĩria andũ akamekĩra hinya, na akamomĩrĩria, na akamahooreria. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũrĩa waragia na rũthiomi nĩ we mwene wĩongagĩrĩra hinya, no ũrĩa ũheanaga ũhoro wa Ngai nĩ kanitha ongagĩrĩra hinya. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 11:29">Ndar 11:29</ref></char></note>No nyende inyuothe mwaragie na thiomi, no makĩria ingĩenda inyuothe mũrathage mohoro. Mũndũ ũrĩa ũrathaga ũhoro nĩakĩrĩte ũrĩa waragia na thiomi, tiga no akorirwo nĩegũtaũra thiomi icio, nĩguo kanitha wongererwo hinya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 14:26">1Akor 14:26</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 6:7">Arom 6:7</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩu, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ingĩũka kũrĩ inyuĩ na njarie na thiomi-rĩ, ingĩmũguna nakĩ, tiga no ndĩmũreheire ũguũrio, kana ũmenyo, kana ũrathi, o na kana kiugo kĩa ũrutani? <verse number="7" style="v"/>O na ha ũhoro ũkoniĩ indo iria itarĩ muoyo iria igambaga, indo ta mũtũrirũ kana kĩnanda kĩa mũgeeto-rĩ, mũndũ angĩgĩkũũrana atĩa rwĩmbo rũrĩa rũrenda kũinwo, tiga hakorirwo na ngũũrani njega ya mĩgambo? <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 10:9">Ndar 10:9</ref></char></note>Ningĩ-rĩ, angĩkorwo karumbeta gatikũruta mũgambo ũgũkũũrĩkana ũrĩa ũkuuga-rĩ, nũũ ũngĩkĩhaarĩria gũthiĩ mbaara-inĩ? <verse number="9" style="v"/>Ũguo noguo ũhoro wanyu ũtariĩ. Tiga mwaririe na ciugo ikũmenyeka na rũthiomi rwanyu-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩkũ ũngĩmenya ũrĩa mũroiga? Mũngĩkorwo o mũkĩarĩria rĩera. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Ti-itherũ nĩ kũrĩ mĩthemba mĩingĩ ya thiomi gũkũ thĩ, no gũtirĩ rũthiomi o na rũmwe rũtarĩ ũrĩa ruugaga. <verse number="11" style="v"/>No angĩkorwo ndingĩmenya ũrĩa mũndũ aroiga-rĩ, niĩ ngĩrĩ mũrũrĩrĩ harĩ mũndũ ũcio ũraaria, nake nĩ mũrũrĩrĩ harĩ niĩ. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 12:1">1Akor 12:1</ref></char></note>Ũguo noguo o na inyuĩ mũtariĩ. Kuona atĩ nĩmwĩrirĩirie mũno iheo cia kĩĩroho-rĩ, kĩgeragiei kuongerera iheo iria ciakaga kanitha ũkagĩa na hinya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Na tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ ũrĩa waragia na rũthiomi rũgeni nĩahooyage nĩguo ahote gũtaũra ũrĩa aroiga. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, ingĩkorwo ndĩrahooya ngĩthiomaga-rĩ, roho wakwa nĩguo ũrahooya, no meciiria makwa matirĩ na maciaro. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:19">Aef 5:19</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, ngũgĩĩka atĩa? Niĩ ndĩrĩhooyaga Ngai na roho wakwa, na ningĩ hooyage na meciiria makwa; o na kũina ndĩrĩinaga na roho wakwa, na ningĩ nyinage na meciiria makwa o namo. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CH 16:36">1Maũ 16:36</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 14:19">Math 14:19</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 11:24">1Akor 11:24</ref></char></note>Ningĩ-rĩ, ũngĩkorwo ũkĩgooca Ngai na roho waku tu-rĩ, mũndũ wa arĩa marĩ gatagatĩ kanyu ũtarataũkĩrwo, angĩkiuga “Ameni” atĩa mahooya-inĩ maku ma gũcookia ngaatho, kuona atĩ ndaramenya ũrĩa ũroiga? <verse number="17" style="v"/>No ũkorwo ũgĩcookia ngaatho wega mũno, no mũndũ ũcio ũngĩ ndanongererwo hinya nĩ ũhoro ũcio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>Nĩngũcookeria Ngai ngaatho nĩgũkorwo niĩ nĩnjaragia na thiomi makĩria manyu inyuothe. <verse number="19" style="v"/>No kanitha-inĩ-rĩ, nĩ kaba njarie ciugo ithano ndĩramenya wega nĩguo ngĩrute andũ arĩa angĩ ũhoro nacio, gũkĩra njarie ciugo ngiri ikũmi cia gũthioma.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 4:14">Aef 4:14</ref>; <ref loc="JER 4:22">Jer 4:22</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 16:19">Arom 16:19</ref></char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, tigagai gwĩciiragia ta ciana. Harĩ ũhoro wa maũndũ marĩa mooru-rĩ, tuĩkai tũkenge, no mwĩciirĩrie-inĩ wanyu mũtuĩke andũ agima. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 10:34">Joh 10:34</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 28:11">Isa 28:11</ref>, <ref loc="ISA 28:12">12</ref></char></note>Thĩinĩ wa Watho nĩ kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Nĩngaarĩria andũ aya</para>
  <para style="q2">na tũnua twa andũ maaragia na thiomi ngʼeni,</para>
  <para style="q1">ndĩmaarĩrie na tũnua twa andũ maaragia na mwarĩrie wa kũngĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">no o na ndeeka ũguo matikanjigua,”</para>
  <para style="qc">ũguo nĩguo Mwathani ekuuga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, kwaria na thiomi nĩ kĩmenyithia kũrĩ andũ arĩa matetĩkĩtie no ti kĩmenyithia kũrĩ arĩa metĩkĩtie; no kũratha ũhoro nĩ kwa arĩa metĩkĩtie, ti kwa arĩa matetĩkĩtie. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:13">Atũm 2:13</ref></char></note>Tondũ ũcio kanitha wothe ũngĩũngana na andũ othe maarie na thiomi-rĩ, na hacooke hatoonye andũ matooĩ ũhoro wa thiomi, kana andũ matetĩkĩtie-rĩ, githĩ matingiuga atĩ mũrĩ agũrũki? <verse number="24" style="v"/>No mũndũ ũtarĩ mwĩtĩkia kana mũndũ ũtarĩ mũtaũkĩre nĩ ũhoro ũcio angĩtoonya rĩrĩa andũ othe mararatha mohoro-rĩ, mũndũ ũcio nĩekũiguithio nĩ andũ othe atĩ nĩ mwĩhia na aciirithio nĩo othe, <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 45:14">Isa 45:14</ref>; <ref loc="ZEC 8:23">Zek 8:23</ref></char></note>na maũndũ marĩa atũire ahithĩte ngoro-inĩ nĩmakoimbũka. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio egũithie thĩ ahooe Ngai, akiugaga atĩrĩ, “Ti-itherũ Ngai arĩ gatagatĩ-inĩ kanyu!”</para>
  <para style="s1">Mahooya Marĩ na Mũtaratara</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:26 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 7:1">Arom 7:1</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 5:19">Aef 5:19</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 12:10">1Akor 12:10</ref></char>
    </note>Tũgũkiuga atĩa, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ? Rĩrĩa muongana hamwe-rĩ, o mũndũ ahota gũkorwo arĩ na rwĩmbo, kana arĩ na ũndũ arenda kũrutana, kana arĩ na ũndũ aguũrĩirio, kana arĩ na thiomi, kana arĩ na ũtaũri wa thiomi. Maũndũ macio mothe no nginya mekagwo nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩkĩra kanitha hinya. <verse number="27" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo nĩ gũkwario na rũthiomi-rĩ, nĩ kwario nĩ andũ eerĩ, na makĩingĩha atatũ, na o mũndũ aarie riita rĩake, na no nginya hagĩe na mũndũ ũngĩ wa gũtaũra. <verse number="28" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo gũtirĩ mũtaũri-rĩ, mwaria ũcio nĩagĩkire arĩ kũu kanitha-inĩ, na akĩĩarĩrie we mwene, na aarĩrie Ngai.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:29 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 12:10">1Akor 12:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Aheani ũhoro eerĩ kana atatũ magĩrĩirwo maarie, nao andũ arĩa angĩ makũũrane wega ũrĩa kũreerwo. <verse number="30" style="v"/>Na mũndũ ũikarĩte thĩ ho angĩgĩa na ũguũrio-rĩ, mwaria ũcio wa mbere nĩakire. <verse number="31" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo inyuothe no mũrathe ũhoro o mũndũ riita rĩake nĩguo andũ othe marutwo maũndũ na momĩrĩrio. <verse number="32" style="v"/>Namo maroho ma anabii nĩmathĩkagĩra anabii o ene. <verse number="33" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:33 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:33">Arom 15:33</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 9:13">Atũm 9:13</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Ngai ti Ngai wa kĩrigiicano no nĩ wa thayũ.</para>
  <para style="p">Ta ũrĩa kũrĩ thĩinĩ wa ciũngano ciothe cia andũ arĩa aamũre, <verse number="34" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:34 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 2:11">1Tim 2:11</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 2:12">12</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 3:16">Kĩam 3:16</ref></char></note>atumia magĩrĩirwo nĩgũikaraga makirĩte ki marĩ thĩinĩ wa kanitha. Matiĩtĩkĩrĩtio kwaria, no nĩmaikarage menyiihĩtie, o ta ũrĩa Watho uugĩte. <verse number="35" style="v"/>Angĩkorwo marĩ na ũndũ mangĩenda kũmenya-rĩ, nĩmoragie athuuri ao ene kwao mũciĩ; nĩgũkorwo nĩ ũndũ ũrĩ thoni atumia kwaragia thĩinĩ wa kanitha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v"/>Hĩ! Anga kiugo kĩa Ngai kĩambĩrĩirie na inyuĩ? Kana hihi no inyuĩ inyuiki gĩakinyĩire? <verse number="37" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:37 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 11:27">Atũm 11:27</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 4:6">1Joh 4:6</ref></char></note>Mũndũ o na ũ angĩĩciiria atĩ nĩ mũnabii, kana arĩ na iheo cia kĩĩroho-rĩ, nĩagĩtĩkĩre atĩ maũndũ maya ndĩramwandĩkĩra nĩ maũndũ marĩa maathanĩtwo nĩ Mwathani. <verse number="38" style="v"/>No angĩagĩra ũndũ ũcio kĩene-rĩ, o nake we mwene nĩakagĩrwo kĩene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">14:39 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 12:31">1Akor 12:31</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 4:11">Aef 4:11</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, mwĩrirĩriei kũrathaga mohoro, na mũtikagiragie ũhoro wa kwaria na thiomi. <verse number="40" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">14:40 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 14:33">1Akor 14:33</ref></char></note>No maũndũ mothe nĩmekagwo na mũtaratara ũrĩa wagĩrĩire, na mekagwo na kĩhaarĩro.</para>
  <chapter number="15" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Kũriũka gwa Kristũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, nĩngwenda kũmũririkania Ũhoro-ũrĩa-mwega ũrĩa ndaamũhunjĩirie, na mũkĩwamũkĩra, na noguo mũtũũrĩte mũrũmĩtie. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Ũhoro ũcio mwega nĩguo ũtũmaga mũhonoke, mwaikara mũrũmĩtie wega ũhoro ũrĩa ndaamũhunjĩirie. Angĩkorwo ti ũguo-rĩ, ũhoro ũcio mwawĩtĩkirie o tũhũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 1:12">Agal 1:12</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 53:5">Isa 53:5</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 24:27">Luk 24:27</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo ũhoro ũrĩa niĩ ndaamũkĩrire nĩguo ndaamũheire, ũrĩ wa mbere na wa bata mũno: atĩ Kristũ nĩakuire nĩ ũndũ wa mehia maitũ o ta ũrĩa Maandĩko moigĩte, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 16:21">Math 16:21</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:25">Atũm 2:25</ref></char></note>na atĩ nĩathikirwo, na atĩ mũthenya wa gatatũ akĩriũkio kũringana na ũrĩa Maandĩko macio moigĩte, <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:34">Luk 24:34</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 16:14">Mar 16:14</ref></char></note>na atĩ akiumĩrĩra Petero, na agĩcooka akiumĩrĩra arĩa Ikũmi na Eerĩ. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Thuutha ũcio, nĩoimĩrĩire makĩria ma ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ magana matano ihinda o rĩmwe, na aingĩ ao marĩ muoyo o na rĩu, o na gũtuĩka amwe ao nĩmarĩkĩtie gũkua. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 1:3">Atũm 1:3</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 1:4">4</ref></char></note>Ningĩ agĩcooka akiumĩrĩra Jakubu na thuutha wa ũguo agĩcooka akiumĩrĩra atũmwo othe, <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 9:3-6">Atũm 9:3-6</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 9:17">17</ref></char></note>na thuutha wa acio angĩ othe akĩnyumĩrĩra o na niĩ, haana ta mũndũ waciarĩtwo atarĩ mũkinyu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:8">Aef 3:8</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 8:3">Atũm 8:3</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo niĩ nĩ niĩ mũnini mũno harĩ atũmwo arĩa angĩ, o na ndiagĩrĩirwo nĩ gwĩtwo mũtũmwo, tondũ nĩndanyariirire kanitha wa Ngai. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 3:24">Arom 3:24</ref>; <ref loc="COL 1:29">Akol 1:29</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:13">Afil 2:13</ref></char></note>No wega wa Ngai nĩguo ũtũmĩte nduĩke ũguo ndariĩ, naguo wega wake kũrĩ niĩ ndwarĩ wa tũhũ. No nĩndarutire wĩra na kĩyo gũkĩra acio angĩ othe, no ti niĩ ndaarutaga wĩra ũcio, no nĩ wega wa Ngai ũrĩa warĩ hamwe na niĩ warutaga wĩra ũcio. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Tondũ ũcio, o na kũngĩtuĩka nĩ niĩ kana nĩ o-rĩ, ũhoro ũyũ noguo tũhunjagia, na noguo inyuĩ mwetĩkirie.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũriũka kwa arĩa Akuũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, kũngĩkorwo kũhunjagio atĩ Kristũ nĩariũkirio akiuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ-rĩ, nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga amwe anyu moige atĩ gũtirĩ kũriũkio kwa arĩa akuũ? <verse number="13" style="v"/>Kũngĩkorwo gũtirĩ kũriũkio kwa arĩa akuũ-rĩ, o nake Kristũ ndaakĩriũkirio. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Na angĩkorwo Kristũ ndaakĩriũkirio-rĩ, kũhunjia gwitũ no gwa tũhũ, nakuo gwĩtĩkia kwanyu no gwa tũhũ. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:24">Atũm 2:24</ref></char></note>Makĩria ma ũguo-rĩ, ithuĩ no tũgĩkorwo tũrĩ aira a Ngai a maheeni, tondũ nĩtuumbũrĩte atĩ Ngai nĩariũkirie Kristũ kuuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ. No rĩrĩ, ndaakĩmũriũkirie angĩkorwo nĩ ma atĩ arĩa akuũ matiriũkagio. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo kũngĩtuĩka atĩ arĩa akuũ matiriũkagio, o nake Kristũ ndaakĩriũkirio. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Na angĩkorwo Kristũ ndaariũkirio-rĩ, gwĩtĩkia kwanyu nĩ gwa tũhũ; mũgĩtũũraga o mehia-inĩ manyu. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ningĩ andũ arĩa marĩkĩtie gũkoma marĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ-rĩ, o nao nĩ kũũra morĩte. <verse number="19" style="v"/>Na kũngĩkorwo kĩĩrĩgĩrĩro giitũ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ no kĩa muoyo-inĩ ũyũ tũrĩ-rĩ, twagĩrĩirwo nĩkũiguĩrwo tha gũkĩra andũ othe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 1:3">1Pet 1:3</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 26:23">Atũm 26:23</ref></char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, ti-itherũ Kristũ nĩariũkĩtio akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, agatuĩka maciaro ma mbere ma arĩa makuĩte. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 5:12">Arom 5:12</ref></char></note>Tondũ-rĩ, o ũrĩa arĩ mũndũ watũmire gĩkuũ gĩũke thĩ, o nakuo kũriũkio kwa arĩa akuũ nĩ mũndũ watũmire gũũke. <verse number="22" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo o ta ũrĩa andũ othe makuaga nĩ ũndũ wa Adamu-rĩ, no taguo andũ othe magaacookio muoyo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 2:19">1Athe 2:19</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 3:23">1Akor 3:23</ref></char></note>No o mũndũ akaariũka ihinda rĩake mwene: Kristũ arĩ we wariũkire mbere; na thuutha andũ arĩa marĩ ake hĩndĩ ĩrĩa agooka. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DAN 7:14">Dan 7:14</ref>, <ref loc="DAN 7:27">27</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:38">Arom 8:38</ref></char></note>Thuutha ũcio nĩguo ihinda rĩa kũrigĩrĩria rĩgaakinya, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa akaaneana ũthamaki kũrĩ Ngai Ithe arĩkĩtie kũniina mothamaki mothe, na wathani, o na hinya wothe. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo no nginya athamake nginya rĩrĩa agaakorwo aigĩte thũ ciake ciothe rungu rwa makinya make. <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="REV 20:14">Kũg 20:14</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, thũ ya mũthia kũniinwo nĩ gĩkuũ. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 8:6">Thab 8:6</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo “nĩ aigĩte indo ciothe rungu rwa makinya make.” Na rĩrĩa gũkwĩrwo atĩ “indo ciothe” nĩciigĩtwo rungu rwake, nĩgũkũmenyeka wega atĩ Ngai we mwene ti wa itari rĩu tondũ nĩ we waigire indo ciothe rungu rwa Kristũ. <verse number="28" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:28 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 3:21">Afil 3:21</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 3:23">1Akor 3:23</ref></char></note>Aarĩkia gwĩka ũguo-rĩ, Mũriũ we mwene nĩagatuĩka wa gwathagwo nĩ ũcio waigire indo ciothe rungu rwake, nĩguo Ngai akorwo nĩ we maũndũ mothe thĩinĩ wa maũndũ mothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, kũngĩkorwo gũtirĩ ũriũkio-rĩ, arĩa mabatithĩtio handũ-inĩ ha arĩa akuũ mageeka atĩa? Angĩkorwo arĩa akuũ matikaariũkio o na atĩa-rĩ, andũ makĩbatithagio handũ-inĩ hao nĩkĩ? <verse number="30" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:30 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:26">2Akor 11:26</ref></char></note>Na ithuĩ-rĩ, twĩtoonyagia ũgwati-inĩ o ithaa o ithaa nĩkĩ? <verse number="31" style="v"/>Ngũmwĩra na ma, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ti-itherũ, o ta ũrĩa ndĩĩrahaga nĩ ũndũ wanyu thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ Mwathani witũ, atĩ niĩ nguaga o mũthenya. <verse number="32" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:32 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 1:8">2Akor 1:8</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 12:19">Luk 12:19</ref></char></note>Angĩkorwo ndaahũũranire na nyamũ cia gĩthaka kũu Efeso nĩ ũndũ wa itũmi cia ũ-mũndũ-rĩ, ndaagunĩkire na kĩ? Angĩkorwo andũ arĩa akuũ matikaariũkio-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q1">“Nĩtũrĩe na tũnyue,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo rũciũ nĩgũkua tũgaakua.”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="33" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:33 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 6:9">1Akor 6:9</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 22:24-25">Thim 22:24-25</ref></char>
    </note>Mũtikaheeneke: “Thiritũ njũru nĩĩthũkagia mĩtugo mĩega.” <verse number="34" style="v"/>Arahũkai mwĩigue ta ũrĩa mwagĩrĩirwo, na mũtigage kwĩhia; nĩgũkorwo andũ amwe matiũĩ Ngai: ndoiga ũguo nĩgeetha ndĩmũconore.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mwĩrĩ ũrĩa Ũkaariũkio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:35 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EZK 37:3">Ezek 37:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No mũndũ ahota kũũria atĩrĩ, “Andũ arĩa akuũ mariũkagio atĩa? Magooka marĩ na mwĩrĩ ũhaana atĩa?” <verse number="36" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:36 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 11:40">Luk 11:40</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 12:24">Joh 12:24</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũrimũ ũrĩkũ ũyũ! Kĩrĩa wahaanda-rĩ, gĩtimeraga gĩtambĩte gũkua. <verse number="37" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa wahaanda-rĩ, ndũhaandaga mwĩrĩ ũrĩa ũgũcooka ũkorwo ho, no gũkorwo ũhaandaga mbeũ ya ngano kana ya kĩndũ kĩngĩ. <verse number="38" style="v"/>No Ngai amĩheaga mwĩrĩ o ũrĩa endaga ĩgĩe naguo, na o mũthemba wa mbegũ akaũhe mwĩrĩ waguo. <verse number="39" style="v"/>Mĩĩrĩ yothe ndĩhaanaine: Andũ marĩ mũthemba ũmwe wa mwĩrĩ, nacio nyamũ mũthemba ũngĩ, na nyoni mũthemba ũngĩ, o nacio thamaki irĩ mwĩrĩ wa mũthemba ũngĩ. <verse number="40" style="v"/>Ningĩ nĩ kũrĩ mĩĩrĩ ya igũrũ na nĩ kũrĩ mĩĩrĩ ya gũkũ thĩ; no riiri wa mĩĩrĩ ya igũrũ nĩ mũthemba ũmwe, na riiri wa mĩĩrĩ ya gũkũ thĩ nĩ mũthemba ũngĩ. <verse number="41" style="v"/>Riũa rĩrĩ na riiri warĩo mwanya, na mweri ũrĩ riiri waguo mwanya, na njata irĩ na riiri wacio mwanya; na njata ĩmwe ĩrĩ riiri ũrĩ ngũũrani na njata ĩrĩa ĩngĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:42 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 13:43">Math 13:43</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ũguo nĩguo gũgaatuĩka hĩndĩ ya kũriũkio kwa andũ arĩa akuũ. Mwĩrĩ ũrĩa ũhaandagwo nĩ wa kũbutha, no ũriũkagio ũtarĩ wa kũbutha; <verse number="43" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:43 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 3:21">Afil 3:21</ref></char></note>mwĩrĩ ũhaandagwo ũrĩ mũmene, ũgacooka ũkariũkio ũrĩ na riiri; ũhaandagwo ũtarĩ na hinya, ũgacooka ũkariũkio ũrĩ na hinya; <verse number="44" style="v"/>ũhaandagwo ũrĩ mwĩrĩ wa ndũire, ũgacooka ũkariũkio ũrĩ mwĩrĩ wa kĩĩroho.</para>
  <para style="p">Angĩkorwo nĩ kũrĩ mwĩrĩ wa ndũire-rĩ, o na mwĩrĩ wa kĩĩroho ũrĩ kuo. <verse number="45" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:45 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 2:7">Kĩam 2:7</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 5:14">Arom 5:14</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio kwandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: “Adamu ũrĩa warĩ mũndũ wa mbere-rĩ, aatuĩkire kĩũmbe kĩrĩ muoyo”; nake Adamu ũrĩa wa kũrigĩrĩria-rĩ, agĩtuĩka roho wa kũheana muoyo. <verse number="46" style="v"/>Mwĩrĩ wa kĩĩroho tiguo waambire gũũka, no nĩ ũrĩa wa ndũire, na thuutha wa ũguo ũgĩũka ũrĩa wa kĩĩroho. <verse number="47" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:47 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 3:19">Kĩam 3:19</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 3:13">Joh 3:13</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 3:31">31</ref></char></note>Mũndũ wa mbere aarĩ wa rũkũngũ rwa thĩ, no mũndũ wa keerĩ oimĩte igũrũ. <verse number="48" style="v"/>O ta ũrĩa mũndũ ũcio wa gũkũ thĩ aatariĩ, noguo arĩa marĩ a tĩĩri matariĩ; na ta ũrĩa mũndũ wa kuuma igũrũ aatariĩ, noguo o na arĩa a igũrũ matariĩ. <verse number="49" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:49 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 5:3">Kĩam 5:3</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 8:29">Arom 8:29</ref></char></note>Na ta ũrĩa twagĩire na mũhianĩre wa mũndũ ũcio wa tĩĩri-rĩ, noguo tũkaagĩa na mũhianĩre wa mũndũ ũcio wa kuuma igũrũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:50 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 6:12">Aef 6:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, mwĩrĩ na thakame itingĩhota kũgaya ũthamaki wa Ngai, kana kĩrĩa kĩbuthaga kĩgae kĩrĩa gĩtabuthaga. <verse number="51" style="v"/>Thikĩrĩriai, ndĩmwĩre ũndũ wa hitho: Tũtigaakua ithuothe, no nĩkũgarũrwo tũkaagarũrwo ithuothe, <verse number="52" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:52 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 24:31">Math 24:31</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 5:25">Joh 5:25</ref></char></note>o kahinda kanini, o ta ibucia rĩa riitho, rĩrĩa karumbeta ka mũthia gakaagamba. Nĩgũkorwo karumbeta nĩgakaahuhwo, nao arĩa akuũ mariũkio matarĩ a kũbutha, na ithuĩ tũgarũrwo mĩĩrĩ. <verse number="53" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:53 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 5:2">2Akor 5:2</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 5:4">4</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo mwĩrĩ ũyũ ũbuthaga no nginya wĩhumbe mwĩrĩ ũtarĩ wa kũbutha, naguo mwĩrĩ ũyũ wa gũkua wĩhumbe mwĩrĩ ũtarĩ wa gũkua. <verse number="54" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">15:54 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 25:8">Isa 25:8</ref></char></note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa kũbutha gũkeehumba kwaga kũbutha, na gũkua kwĩhumbe kwaga gũkua-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩyo ũhoro nĩũkahinga ũrĩa wandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ, “Gĩkuũ nĩkĩniinĩtwo gĩgatoorio biũ.”</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="55" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:55 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HOS 13:14">Hos 13:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Wee gĩkuũ-rĩ, gũtoorania gwaku gũkĩrĩ ha?</para>
  <para style="q2">Wee gĩkuũ-rĩ, rũboora rwaku rũkĩrĩ ha?”</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="56" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">15:56 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 4:15">Arom 4:15</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rũboora rwa gĩkuũ nĩ mehia, naguo hinya wa mehia uumanaga na watho. <verse number="57" style="v"/>No rĩrĩ, Ngai arogaathwo nĩgũkorwo nĩwe ũtũheaga ũtooria thĩinĩ wa Mwathani witũ Jesũ Kristũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="58" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ arĩa nyenda, ikaragai mwĩhaandĩte wega. Mũtikanenyenyio nĩ ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ. Tũũrai mwĩheanĩte kũna wĩra-inĩ wa Mwathani, tondũ nĩmũũĩ atĩ wĩra wanyu thĩinĩ wa Mwathani ti wa tũhũ.</para>
  <chapter number="16" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mũhothi nĩ ũndũ wa Andũ a Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 24:17">Atũm 24:17</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 9:13">Atũm 9:13</ref></char>
    </note>Na rĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa mũhothi nĩ ũndũ wa andũ a Ngai ũtariĩ ũũ: Ĩkagai ũrĩa ndeerire makanitha ma Galatia mekage. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 20:7">Atũm 20:7</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 9:4-5">2Akor 9:4-5</ref></char></note>Mũthenya wa mbere wa kiumia-rĩ, o mũndũ wanyu nĩagĩrĩirwo nĩkũigaga mbeeca ta ũrĩa ũthũkũmi wake ũigana, agaciigaga, nĩguo hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ngooka kũu gũtikanagĩe na mũhothi. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Na ndaakinya-rĩ, andũ arĩa mũgaakorwo mũgathĩrĩirie nĩngamahe marũa ma kũmamenyithania na ndĩmatũme Jerusalemu na iheo cianyu. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Na kũngĩkoneka kwagĩrĩire o na niĩ thiĩ-rĩ, nĩngatwarana nao.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ndũmĩrĩri cia Mwanya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 4:19">1Akor 4:19</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 6:9">Atũm 6:9</ref></char>
    </note>Ndaarĩkia gũtuĩkanĩria Makedonia-rĩ, nĩgũkorwo nĩngatuĩkanĩria kuo, nĩngooka kũrĩ inyuĩ. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Hihi ngaikara na inyuĩ gwa kahinda, o na kana njikare kũu hĩndĩ ya heho yothe, nĩguo mũkaahota kũndeithĩrĩria gũthiĩ rũgendo-inĩ rwakwa kũrĩa guothe ngaathiĩ. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:21">Atũm 18:21</ref></char></note>Ndikwenda kuonana na inyuĩ hĩndĩ ĩno ndĩrahĩtũkĩra kũu, tondũ ngwĩhoka atĩ nĩtũgaikarania na inyuĩ kwa ihinda, Mwathani etĩkĩra. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:19">Atũm 18:19</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:1">Atũm 2:1</ref></char></note>No nĩngũikara gũkũ Efeso nginya hĩndĩ ya Bendegothito, <verse number="9" style="v"/>tondũ ndĩmũhingũrĩre mweke mũnene wa kũruta wĩra mwega ũrĩ na uumithio, no nacio thũ nĩ nyingĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 16:1">Atũm 16:1</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 15:58">1Akor 15:58</ref></char>
    </note>Timotheo angĩũka-rĩ, menyererai nĩguo aikare kũu na inyuĩ atarĩ na guoya, nĩgũkorwo nĩ wĩra wa Mwathani araruta, o ta ũrĩa ndĩraruta. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 4:12">1Tim 4:12</ref>; <ref loc="2CO 1:16">2Akor 1:16</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 15:33">Atũm 15:33</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, gũtirĩ mũndũ wagĩrĩirwo nĩ kwaga kũmwamũkĩra. Mumagariei na thayũ nĩgeetha akinye kũrĩ niĩ. Nĩndĩmwetereire marĩ hamwe na ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>Na rĩrĩ, ha ũhoro ũkoniĩ mũrũ wa Ithe witũ Apolo-rĩ: nĩndamũringĩrĩirie mũno ooke kũrĩ inyuĩ arĩ hamwe na ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ. Nowe ndeendaga gũũka ihinda rĩu, no nĩarĩũka aagĩa na mweke.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 1:27">Afil 1:27</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 6:10">Aef 6:10</ref></char>
    </note>Ikaragai mwĩhũgĩte, na mwĩhaande mũrũmĩte wega thĩinĩ wa wĩtĩkio; ningĩ mũtuĩke andũ omĩrĩru; na mũgĩe na hinya. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Ĩkagai maũndũ mothe mũrĩ na wendani.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Inyuĩ nĩmũũĩ atĩ andũ a nyũmba ya Stefana nĩo maarĩ a mbere gwĩtĩkia kũu bũrũri wa Akaia, na nĩmerutĩire gũtungatagĩra andũ arĩa aamũre. Nĩngũkĩmũringĩrĩria, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, <verse number="16" style="v"/>mwathĩkagĩre andũ ta acio, na mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũrutithanagia wĩra na ithuĩ, akĩũnogagĩra. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:9">2Akor 11:9</ref></char></note>Nĩndakenire rĩrĩa Stefana, marĩ na Fotunato, na Akaiko maakinyire, nĩ ũndũ nĩo maahingĩirie ũndũ ũrĩa itaarĩ naguo kuuma kũrĩ inyuĩ. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">16:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 15:32">Arom 15:32</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:29">Afil 2:29</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩmacanjamũrire roho wakwa o na wanyu. Andũ ta acio nĩmagĩrĩirwo kũheagwo gĩtĩĩo.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngeithi cia Mũthia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 18:2">Atũm 18:2</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 16:5">Arom 16:5</ref></char>
    </note>Makanitha ma bũrũri wa Asia nĩmamũgeithia. Akula na Pirisila nĩmamũgeithia mũno thĩinĩ wa Mwathani, o na kanitha ũrĩa ũcemanagia kwao nyũmba nĩwamũgeithia. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ othe arĩa marĩ gũkũ nĩmamũgeithia. O mũndũ nĩageithie ũrĩa ũngĩ na ngeithi theru cia kĩmumunyano.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v"/>Niĩ, Paũlũ, nĩ niĩ ndandĩka ngeithi ici na guoko gwakwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 6:24">Aef 6:24</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 9:3">Arom 9:3</ref>; <ref loc="REV 22:20">Kũg 22:20</ref></char>
    </note>Angĩkorwo he mũndũ o na ũ ũtendete Mwathani-rĩ, arogwatwo nĩ kĩrumi. Ũka, Mwathani!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">16:23 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 16:20">Arom 16:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Wega wa Mwathani Jesũ ũroikara na inyuĩ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v"/>Wendani wakwa ũromũkinyĩra inyuĩ inyuothe mũrĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ. Ameni.</para>
</usx>
